Lu Jie sets out to study the immutable truths hidden within the world, and soon finds an allnew path of cultivation that could take him to the very top.Art by Kisai Entertainment

title: The Count's Secret Maid
author: TON,MIDNIGHT STUDIO,Baekjua
synopsis: For Paula, not a single day passed by without a reminder of her ugliness. But it was her hideous face that spared her from being sold to a brothel or dying tragically like her sisters. So when Paula's father sells her off to work at an esteemed nobleman's mansion, she realizes that peasant girls are a disposable resource. However, she finds the young Count Belunita tucked away in an annex, shamefully hidden from the curious eyes of the public. And as Paula struggles to appeal to her tyrannical master's whims, she must also embrace her role as his secret maid.

title: The Heir
author: Dongwoo Han,Dohee Lee
synopsis: As a young boy, Taeha Jin life is turned upside down when an attack during a family yacht trip robs him of his parents and future as heir to the Cheongu GroupKorea leading conglomerate. Uncovering the dark truths behind the accidentone of vicious power struggles and family betrayalshe escapes to Italy, vowing revenge. Seventeen years later, Taeha is finally back in Korea. A man driven by vengeance, he can wait for the sweetest revenge as he makes those who robbed everything from him pay dearly. The stakes are high, and the battle with Cheongu begins!

title: At Your Mercy
author: Team Lightsalt,Team honeybread,Early Flower
synopsis: Getting transported into a novel once? Unusual. Twice? Welcome to Jian Han reality. Her second possession lands her in the body of a noble lady with an unfortunate reputation the court fool. While still adjusting to this twist of fate, the enigmatic Crown Prince Iskan enters the scene with an unsettling proposition: "Take me as yours," he says, "Ill become your most cherished possession." Between her reputation as a fool and a prince whose motives remain unclear, can Jian navigate this complicated new reality?

title: A Savage Proposal
author: Lee yuna,team IRUKA
synopsis: When the ruthless Lord Tiwakan seizes the kingdom of Nauk, Princess Liene Arsac faces an impossible choice: marry her captor or watch her homeland crumble. But Lord Tiwakan isn just after power; he desires Liene, and his devotion stirs a mix of fear and undeniable attraction within her. With her former betrothed, Lafitte, still missing, Liene must decide whether to trust Tiwakan's promises or hold out hope for a rescue. As dangerous secrets come to light, Liene decision could change the fate of Nauk and her own heart forever.

title: Dagger to the Heart
author: oori_
synopsis: How hard is it to kill a princess? Rafael, a cocky assassin, takes on a job to kill Sazet, the princess of the empire, but soon finds that she is not the easy target he thought. When they are forced to team up, Rafael must decide if he will bury his dagger in her heart. Or if his will be captured first.

title: When Two Villains Meet
author: Lim Hayam,Sark,ssogariii
synopsis: Atalante is the boss of a notorious organization that works in the empire shadow. One day, she receives a request from the emperor to assassinate a new target: the tyrant archduke Lionel Vianc.Reluctantly leaving behind her simple life with her members, Atalante heads off to perform the assassination, but for some reason the archduke doesn die.After a mixup between a love potion and poison, Atalante finds herself in a frustrating predicament as the tyrant archduke not only refuses to die but has also fallen in love with her!

title: My Avatars Path to Greatness
author: TestSample,LICO,HANSA
synopsis: Seonghyeon Han is a victim of a violent crime that left him with impaired legs and a fear of the outside world. Now, he faces an even greater challenge: while he gained the power to create clones, he has just 24 hours before being sent to another dimension. As the countdown ticks down, Seonghyeon makes a desperate move he sends his clone through the interdimensional portal, and discovers his real body can remain safe at home. Thus begins the epic tale of Seonghyeon's clones.

title: My Blood-Curdling Campus Life
author: NIMNI
synopsis: A cute guy with an angelic face? Check. A cold and aloof outsider with a cat? Check. A class full of vampires? Check Wait, what? All her life, Seonha Shin has lived in the shadow of her sister, Seonghye, who is one year older than her. Luckily, there is one thing Seonha does better than her sister donating blood! When Seonha gets special admission into a prestigious university as a blood donor, she finally starts to feel like the main character of her life. Little did she know she'd be surrounded by vampires!

title: Duchess in Ruins
author: Candlebambi,Saedle,Lemon Frog
synopsis: Edele Lancaster is the perfect noble lady who has been groomed for the job. But when her husband whom she married reluctantly commits treason, she is branded a traitor and becomes a slave. Distraught, she tries to kill herself to preserve honor as a noble lady, but her new master, Count Laslo Krissus prevents her from doing so. Will Edele be able to find freedom and happiness in her new life as Count Krissus maid?

title: Code Demon
author: MelsPlace,Black BAM Studio
synopsis: Forced to take over his family technology company, struggling college student Kaito agrees to the terms of a seemingly harmless video game meant to be an online tutorial for IT, only to realize too late that he become a contestant in a battle royale where hell fight to win a passing gradeor die trying.

title: The Death of Kindness
author: Skeleton_House
synopsis: After the mysterious murder of his parents, Yoichi Sakagami struggled to live a normal life taking care of his young siblings. The only way he survived was by exploiting a mysterious ability he had to regenerate his organs. But when shadowy forces come after him, he'll find that there's more to his ability than he thought. Will he be able to control it to get his revenge and protect those he cares about? Or will the power he has control him instead?

title: My Daddy is a Villain!
author: mono_krm
synopsis: The daily life of villainous and feared Lord Anathema and his daughter, Desdemona, as they temporarily reside in the realm of Earth.

title: Love and Other Wicked Things
author: Thabfu,Philline Harms,Dominique Riley
synopsis: Rhia Greenbrook is a witch from a long line of earth witches in the sleepy town of Oakriver. Even though she can practice divination like the rest of her family, she always embraced the traditions of the secret magical world she grown up in.That is, until Valerie a cute, bold fire witch who excels in divination comes to town looking for answers about her mother disappearance.With their fates now intertwined, a dark presence looms over Oakriver, and it up to Rhia to tap into the full potential of her magic to save the town she loves

title: Adopting a Zombie
author: _gwagj
synopsis: When a failed scientist falls in love with the zombie he's studying for a cure.

title: Worth the Candle
author: Alexander Wales,Betofu,Tristan Bellawala,WmW
synopsis: Juniper was always the Dungeon Master, never the player. He was always a creator of worlds rather than the one who walked within themuntil now.Somehow, the tables have turned in the most dramatic way possible. Juniper finds himself in a world filled with the wildest fantasies a mind could come up with, and his fingerprints are all over it.Throughout this world, echoes of his own ideas and plots leave him feeling like he always one step behind. He finds bits and pieces of ancient influence strewn about every town he goes through. One thing is clear, though: Juniper walks this magical new world in someone else shadow.It might all add up to something vitalif only he can survive long enough to figure it out.

title: Surprise You're Gay!
author: laundromat&lawnmower
synopsis: Some are born gay, some achieve gayness, and some have gayness thrust upon them.Sebastian has failed his Intro to Computer Science class two times already and now only has one more chance to pass. What can he do but ask Bianca, a local college scammer, to take his place for the entire semester? Will she be able to fool a professor who has met Sebastian before? Not to mention, what will happen when a girl named Chandler starts to develop a crush on Sebastian A.K.A. Bianca? Bianca life is soon to be filled with drama, but she has no time for that. No, Bianca only has one goal Don get caught. (A retelling of Shakespeare classic play, Twelfth Night.)

title: New Magical Me
author: Prinnstar,Chuuney,Greenie_Olivelie
synopsis: Erika is the city's strongest Magical Girl and leader of the dazzling Star Chroma group! But when she sacrifices herself to defeat the terrifying Spore Queen Miasma, it's up to her best friend Winnie to pick up the pieces. Or in this case, fall to pieces. 8 years later and Star Chroma is no more and Winnie is stuck in a dead end office job. But when the Spore Queen unexpectedly returns, Winnie will have to find a way to manage on her own. At least until an old friend reappears as well

title: The Villainous Tyrant has Returned
author: Studio wooridle,Jepure
synopsis: Was there ever a greater tragedy than love turned to hate? Such is the tragic downfall of Emperor Ludwig of Berzantium, as he is betrayed and murdered in a fiery blaze by his empress. Olive Charleterre was once a bright young debutante, until her spirit was broken by the emperor cruelty. Yet when Ludwig opens his eyes, he finds he has been sent back in time to his childhood. Whether he uses this boon to reclaim his lost love and forge a new path away from his villainous future only time will tell.

title: The Empress Two Wolves
author: LICO,Honey Bambi
synopsis: In a world where destiny is branded on their skin, Sepia, the human empress of the beastkin empire, is threatened by a new rival: Titie, a white deer, with Demios the emperor name emblazoned on her chest. Amidst Titie malicious attempts, Sepia clings to her role as empress and the Star of Ishtar, determined to fulfill her destiny as the empire savior. Enter Roxan, a wolf beastkin and cousin to Demois, whose allure stirs Sepia feelings. In a web of love, loyalty, and deception, can Sepia reclaim her power and discover the truth of her heart?

title: Void Man
author: KEON
synopsis: Gods have descended upon the world, and Dail's ready to drag them all to hell. After the lives of his loved ones were taken by the gods, Dail offers his soul in exchange for the powers of the very killer of gods, the Void.

title: Absolute Regression
author: JP,PARK JIN HWAN,Y.H.JANG
synopsis: The past has changed, but like a fiery comet, he still comes. Mugi Hwa, the one without equal, slashed through Murim's skies with his sword, toppling every lord who dared to face himeven Cheonma, Mugeuk Geom father. But Mugeuk didn accept defeat. Instead, he turned to the forbidden: a timebending ritual that hurled him into his own past. Now, retracing his steps, he races against the clock until Mugi emerges once again. But this time, it's not just about power, but mending old wounds and forging new bonds to unite his people and prepare for the bloodtide to come.

title: You Just Made My Day
author: yejo
synopsis: The transfer student Yebom was jealous of Eunho, an honor student everyone liked. Many years later, Yebom life feels hopeless and bleak when one day, she finally learns about the reason behind Eunho death that occurred a long time ago. Yebom, filled with regret, returns to the time when she was 18 and faces him once again. What drove the seemingly perfect boy to death? Yebom is finally ready to hear Eunho story. This series contains themes regarding suicide and bullying that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Special Civil Servant
author: Kwon Sora,Seo Jaewon,ch
synopsis: Sociallyawkward Maru Han bombs his fifth attempt at getting a dream job in the civil service. But after a strange creature attacks him in the mountains, he finds himself recruited into the Special Civil Service for the Ministry of Environment. This secret organization is dedicated to fighting nachal, humandevouring demons who appear in clouds of yellow dust. As Maru struggles in his new job fighting nachal, he must find out why they're mysteriously drawn to him before the prophesied end of the world arrives.

title: Juvenile Detention Center
author: Chungmin,Lee Soo hyon
synopsis: Juyeong is in a juvenile detention center for the attempted murder of his father, Gangryong. He clings to hope, dreaming of a future in Seoul with his childhood friend, Dayeon. But everything shatters when Dayeon is tragically killed by a rogue truck, and the devastation deepens when Juyeong learns that his father was behind the wheel.In a cruel twist, Gangryong regains consciousness and offers Juyeong an ultimatum: If you want revenge, become the king of this detention center!Now, Juyeong must navigate the treacherous world of prison politics, determined to rise to power and avenge his friend.

title: Back to Chanbi
author: jang sawhee
synopsis: Gyeono Kang, a lucky high schooler, used to enjoy the mutual love he shared with the prettiest girl in his class, Chanbi Baek. She was always all about him until an accident wiped her memories of the past year, and just like that, she no longer had feelings for him. But what about Gyeono, whose heart still beats for her? Is it even possible to win her back? Did she really like him back to begin with?! Somebody help!

title: The Masters Have Subscribed
author: DN,kangho HA,KIM KI BAEK
synopsis: Cheongun, parry the attack! Move faster or the obstacle course will kill you!The progenitors of the great Wudang sect and the mighty Shaolin encounter postascension issues when they find themselves reduced to servants in the godly realm. Their only hope and escape from their divine chores lie in the hands of lessthanaverage.Cheongun, who can hardly beat his peers in the sect. Can the masters raise an average boy into a master of martial arts and finally relieve themselves of their menial chores?

title: The Flower That Swallowed the Beast
author: Mrang,Dalchun,baekmyo
synopsis: A bargain for her life, to escape a tragic future. When Iris Whittle is murdered by her sadistic husband, she is sent back in time to when she was 20 years old. As the unwanted daughter of a duke, Iris realizes she can leverage her status and foresight to secure a better life this time around. Thus, Iris makes a daring marriage proposal to the fearsome Count Keibrandt Green, the most eligible bachelor of Gavizar Empire, whose gruff and stern demeanor hides the fangs of a wolf.

title: Who That Long-Haired Senior?
author: bullgwanhu
synopsis: Sol Song has a uniquely quirky taste in men: they absolutely must have long hair. Otherwise, she sees them as literal "stone heads," devoid of facial features. So, when her first love and the only longhaired guy on campus shows up with a buzz cut, she's devastated. But as they start to reconnect and emotions deepen, Sol must discover whether she likes Okseok for who he truly is or just for his hair.

title: To Die or To Fall In Love
author: HONEYB
synopsis: Isabella Woodville has always lived in her sister shadow, but her life takes a dark turn when she witnesses a murder at a masquerade ball. Targeted by a masked serial killer after receiving the notorious black invitation, she kidnapped and brought to a cursed estate. The twisted wager? Fall in love with him within 15 days, and she dies. Resist, and she survives. Caught in a deadly game of love and survival, Isabella must navigate the line between reality and the seductive fantasy she been thrown into.

title: The New Hire Secret
author: Dasim,Gogigamza,blancD
synopsis: With a handsome face and manners that would put a diplomat to shame, new hire Hyeonu Lee is a sight for sore eyes to Senior Manager Iyeon Shin when he walks through the doors of Hanshin Worldwide. Feeling like she won the lottery, Iyeon is looking forward to her company life alongside this polite and hardworking young man.Hey, Iyeon. Get this done by tomorrow.Hyeonu is no regular employee; he the son of the CEO. And as he begins to show his true nasty nature behind closed doors, Iyeon begins wondering what she did to deserve him.

title: A Knight With a Time Limit
author: GEUMUIHAENG,KDRM,Yunyeol Choi
synopsis: Leaving behind his miserable life and untimely death,Luis Cloyde is reborn into a new world filled with fantastical beasts and adventure.The catch? He must continue killing other living beings to extend his own life.But given a second chance at life, Luis Cloyde is willing to do just about anything to survive.

title: Starting Over With the Dead You
author: Hiwoo
synopsis: When Iru starts college, she unexpectedly meets Haim, a guy who looks just like Hayul the one who used to torment her as a child. She feels uneasy around him yet finds herself drawn to his seemingly perfect nature. Is it really okay for her to open up her heart to him?

title: 3X3!
author: MNYujacha
synopsis: Menage a trois? More like menace a trois! As a bashful, introverted BL lover, all Minji Kim ever wanted for her final year of middle school was to be left alone to draw dinosaurthemed superhero smut Ahem, tasteful fanfiction. So exactly how she became part of the socalled Future Vision Club with school rebel Haein Shin and straightlaced student Jisu Han, shell never quite understand. The only thing that clear is that the year ahead promises to be unforgettable, to say the least! So, prepare for trouble and make it triple?

title: The Barbarian of Seoul Station
author: LICO,Jin Seol woo
synopsis: Cheoldu, a barbarian raised on Earth, lives a mundane life with his best friend Jintae. But when he sees an alien creature from his planet on the news, everything changes. Thrown into an apocalyptic challenge, Cheoldu and Jintae must adjust their lives in Nova, a savage world filled with goblins and ogres. Will the two conquer Nova perils and uncover the secrets that could change Earth fate? An epic tale of friendship, survival, and untamed adventure awaits.

title: Cinderelle
author: troyzworld
synopsis: Giselle should support the royal engagement she's the princess's best friend, after all! But it's hard to watch your love get married to someone else. What's a girl to do? Team up with the one other person in the kingdom not celebrating the marriage: a handsome rogue who wants the princess' fiance dead. When Giselle learns the engagement is not what it seems, she's willing to get her hands dirty. Can a noble lady and a street rat stop this courtship from sailing?

title: A Practical Guide to Evil
author: David Verburg,Yeajin Shin,Yui,G. Galen Mayhew,WmW
synopsis: The Empire stands triumphant.For twenty years the Dread Empress has ruled over the lands that were once the Kingdom of Callow, but behind the scenes of this dawning golden age threats to the crown are rising. The nobles of the Wasteland weave their plots behind pleasant smiles while rebellion stirs beyond Peren Woods, for dreams of crowns were buried in shallow graves.The greatest danger of all lies to the west, where the First Prince of Procer restored order at last: her people sundered, she ponders if a crusade might not be the way to secure her reign. Yet none of this matters, for in the heart of the conquered lands the most dangerous man alive sat across an orphan girl and offered her a knife.Her name is Catherine Foundling, and she has a plan.

title: Angel Wings
author: Brandon Chen,Comipa
synopsis: Angels ferry the good souls to Heaven. Devils ferry the bad souls to Hell. That is how the afterlife is written. Evangeline was born a Devil, but has always dreamed of becoming an Angel and helping souls live a beautiful afterlife. When she encounters Tatrasiel, an Angel curious of Hell, she proposes the impossible: switching lives to see how the other lives! But they'll soon discover Heaven and Hell isn't quite what either of them expected!

title: Academy of Marginalized Superpowers
author: jeffuwnag
synopsis: In a world of people gifted with supernatural abilities, a boy with a power deemed marginal by society navigates life surrounded by his marginally extraordinary peers.

title: stare down.
author: soycisoy
synopsis: The story of Nil, who misconstrues an enamoured stare. And the story of Pas, who plays along in hope of something more.

title: Say the Right Thing
author: SammyMontoya
synopsis: On your arm are the first words your soulmate will ever say to you. Sometimes they're nice. Sometimes they're vague. Sometimes they're "Watch it, Jackass." And sometimes your soulmate is a wanted felon and also magic, which Seth discovers when he meets his soulmate, Errol, an alleged dark mage on the run. Oh well.

title: Angel of Death
author: Riley Redgate,Mhaikkun
synopsis: When Azriel the fearsome and unfeeling Angel of Death allows a human soul to slip through his fingers, God casts him down to Earth to find it. Azriel plans to use Jo LeCourt, the sister of the woman whose soul he failed to reap, to guide him. But he not counting on the sharpwitted and relentless Jo, who knows why he's there and will stop at nothing to stop him.As the two circle each other, Azriel discovers, for the first time in eternity, someone who really challenges and interests him. And Jo discovers, for the first time in her life, someone as reliable and exacting as she is. Neither of them are expecting to find a lovethat will change them forever.

title: Seabird and the Wolf
author: Kisai Entertainment,Gleecat,ricepupa,Miss Xero,Mang Morning
synopsis: Chosen by the last remaining Seabird, Lott has been cursed with a target on her back. After the notorious Woohoppiage pirates pillage her village and kidnap her sister, she embarks on a perilous journey to get her back. And shell do whatever it takes to make that happen, even if that means joining the Black Ocean crew and pretending to be a man. But she's not the only one with a secret on this pirate ship

title: My Beloved Emperor
author: Chi Coi
synopsis: In a distant empire, the young Emperor is consumed by his duties, yet the people whisper that he overdue for marriage. When Tran, a spirited workingclass woman, unexpectedly saves the Emperor disguised and in danger their unlikely friendship ignites into a daring romance. As they face formidable enemies determined to thwart the Emperor reign, together they craft a legacy that redefines the future of the empire.

title: Amelia the Level Zero Hero
author: MelasDelta,Kisai Entertainment,Azrie
synopsis: Who needs a Class when you're already the strongest anyways? Ten years ago, Amelia woke up in a broken world where she had to fight for her survival. Now, after defeating the Void itself and escaping the abyss, she's finally found her way back into the real world. But instead of returning to Earth, she arrives in Vacuos a fantasy world governed by a System as if it were a video game. And when rewarded with a Class befitting her accomplishments to become a powerful Hero that will forever dedicate her life to protecting this world that is not her own she only has one response. Absolutely not. Im going to live a normal life now, thank you very much.

title: Enoch: The Shining Tree
author: Chiroyugo
synopsis: "You shall live and suffer for eternity, trapped within your armor, prisoners of time."Enoch's life is turned upside down when his entire family is slaughtered overnight by the cursed knights.The knights wander, sentenced by the witch's curse to a fate of endless empty slaughters.Enoch trampled under their trail of blood, burns for a vengeance that outlasts, outdoes eternity.Who will be whose fate? Who is the one that orchestrates their conflicting fates?

title: Light of Arad: Forerunner
author: jegalbokja,funkycreature,Respect
synopsis: Jinseong streams the online action game Dungeon and Fighter for a living, and while assisting a ranger, he ends up doing exactly what the player warned him not to helping him fight the boss. Little did Jinseong know that the ranger was a person sucked into the game world, and was now dead for failing his mission. Transported into the world of DNF to take responsibility, Jinseong must work his way through the quest line as a Dark Knight to stop the contamination from leading players astray and destroying the world of Arad. Will he make it through alive?

title: My Girlfriend
author: Park_ci
synopsis: One day, Jio is horrified to witness his girlfriend, Miho, devouring human flesh. How could this be happening? He's struggling to understand the events that transpired when Miho killed his close buddy. Jio flees in panic, only to run into his friend whom he was sure was dead still alive. Jio grapples with doubt, struggling to maintain his grip on sanity. Is Miho really the monster, or is everything just a horrible nightmare?

title: Asura
author: Giun Ryu,Mun Jeong Hoo
synopsis: Once there was an emperor vassal who journeyed abroad to discover the secret of immortality. A lifetime went by, and the emperor and empire fell to dust. The vassal, now known as Chief, returns to the realm, bringing with him a boy of mysterious origin and immense power named Asura. In this unfamiliar world, Chief and Asura must reckon with peril and unrest among martial arts sects ruled by the nefarious Fort Sovereign. One thing, however, is for certain: the realm will never be the same.

title: Humanoido
author: hyung ju
synopsis: Meet Ido Noh, a shy firstyear high school student with a severe stutter that makes talking to people nearly impossible. Her life changes when she meets Sei Ryu, a robot with a mysterious past and a quest to reclaim his lost memories. Can Ido find her voice with this unlikely friend, and will Sei uncover the secrets of his origin?

title: Phantom Whispers
author: moonkyoung kim
synopsis: Noa has struggled with hearing unsettling voices since she was a child. But when a mysterious murder takes place, the voice in Noa head urges her to uncover the killer. With the police skeptical and her sanity on the line, Noa must navigate a web of fear and suspicion, guided by a ghost, to catch a ruthless killer before she herself becomes the serial killer. Will Noa uncover the murderer, or will her own mind betray her?This series contains themes regarding mental health and violence that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Seasons of Lovesome
author: HONGDUCK,NEMONE
synopsis: Life isn always perfect, but love certainly makes it better. The exciting tale of young love continues a year following the story Seasons of Blossom.Bomi and her university classmate Pureum lives center around a new place, Cafe Blossom & Nemone Art Studio,as they navigate the joy and hardships of university and professional life.

title: I Became a Level 999 Demon Queen
author: LEE JAEI,Hangaga,SANSOBEE
synopsis: The terminally ill daughter of a poor family is given a new lease on life when she is granted the chance to be reborn as anyone she wants. But her plans go awry when she accidentally wishes to become the wrong character of the video game she likes Raina Rubellite, the final evil boss that torments the righteous main character of the game The Power of Love. Now, our protagonist finds herself reborn as an evil devil queen with overpowered dark magic powers, but she won let the video game plot stop her from living the life of her dreams!

title: The Villainess Just Wants to Live in Peace!
author: Graycat,Honaran,Lee Harin
synopsis: I quit my terrible job and set off on a trip, only to die in a plane crash! I woke up to find myself reincarnated as Tanasia Breloff, the villainess of a novel I once read. Tanasia was scheming to harm her sister out of jealousy, but Im not interested in villainy; Im content being a beautiful, wealthy noblewoman! But wait don I eventually get killed in the novel? I must prevent my death so I can live the peaceful life Ive dreamed of! This series contains themes regarding abuse and may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised.

title: Changing the Genre From Angst to Heartwarming
author: Hwang DoTol,Ryuho,Yangdam
synopsis: I've been reincarnated. Into a novel I used to enjoy in my past life, no less!My name is Renatis, and I'll be playing the part of little sister to the female lead in this dark, tragic whirlwind of a story where a beastly bad boy shatters my sister's hopes, dreams, and her life. My sister is too good and too beautiful, and I'm not about to let that happen to my perfect sister.So, I'm taking charge. I shall turn this dark, tragic story into a heartwarming tale of healing. I will save my sister.This series contains themes regarding child abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/)."

title: JAKDU: Shaman's Blade
author: 232,POGO
synopsis: Yongjin is a struggling orphana blunt realist with no time or money to spare on superstitious nonsense. But on his 16th birthday, he finds his life taking a dramatic turn when his classmate Huisu, whom he had never interacted with before, suddenly asks to be his girlfriend. For the first time, Yongjin isn alonebut his new company isn exactly the kind he had always wished for, as he finds himself being chased by spirits instead! Though this wasn quite the sweet sixteen he had in mind, Yongjin must now navigate through a new world he never thought existed.

title: DevilUp
author: VoyceMe Inc.
synopsis: Silas Reinheart has lost his family and the love of his life, only to awaken in hell facing the consequences of his dying words. He had cursed the gods and blamed them for the horrors struck upon his village, dooming him to an eternity of torment. But when a Devil offers Silas a deal, his fate is altered allowing him to return to the world of the living and collect souls as the Devil Spawn. If Silas refuses, he and his loved ones will be lost for eternity, however if he accepts the Devil contract there is a chance he can save the souls of those he lost.

title: Duolingo Unleashed
author: Karen Buchanan,Kylie "Kole" Hunsinger
synopsis: Overwhelmed by his growing workload, Duo the Owl seeks an assistant. When his search leads him to a free clone machine, he thinks all his problems are solved after all, who better to help Duo than Duo? But when Duo grand ambitions blow up in his face (literally) and wayward clones start terrorizing the city, it up to Duo and his crew to restore order and more importantly, his reputation! Buckle up for a new adventure that questions what it truly means to be yourself.

title: I Killed the Main Player
author: GREENKYRIN,HELP.ME
synopsis: Being a character of your favorite game is great! Sure, he just a minor NPC, but Corin knows this game like the back of his hand. With his knowledge and the main player Sihu abilities, everything going smoothly until Corin discovers Sihu been murdering innocent NPCs and stealing their items. Horrified but powerless to stop him, Corin awaits the end of the game only for Sihu to mysteriously fail at the last mission. Instantly, Corin travels three years back in time. Now, he determined to kill Sihu and take on his role defeat the final boss and save the world.

title: Too Late for Regrets
author: Jiyeop,Dalseul
synopsis: The tale of Princess Ines is a tragic one. Born a royal of the Zener Empire, she is reviled and neglected as a child born out of wedlock. To compound her misfortune, Ines is married off to Grand Duke Ryan of Eleanor, a renowned war hero of the Lezan Empire who fought against Zener. Ryan proves a stern and distant husband to Ines, and she soon determines that she must fight for a life of dignity if not in Eleanor, then elsewhere. Thus begins a marriage of emotional reserve and regrets

title: Tales of the Unusual 2
author: Seongdae Oh
synopsis: From twisted games of evil demons and the roaming of the undead to strange technology that makes the impossible happen, dive into Tales of the Unusual 2, another thrilling collection of supernatural horror stories that will have you scrolling for hours. With just the right balance of dark humor and the unexpected, each short story pulls you into a new immersive world and unravels plot twists you never would've imagined. Just remember, there's nothing to be afraid of If you have nothing to hide.

title: Banhyang: The Remote Island
author: PIGGY
synopsis: Sehim field trip to Banhyang Island takes an ominous turn when a fierce storm leaves everyone stranded. As three students inexplicably vanish amidst the storm, Sehim and his friends scramble to find out why. But, their desperate efforts only seem to drag them deeper into the island sinister secrets every revelation intensifying the chilling forces lurking on the island, their chances of leaving the island seem uncertain by the day.

title: A Life-Changing Turn
author: Gwangjin,Ghna,YOPY
synopsis: My name is Sua Jo, and my life couldn't get any better my loving dad is a Mayor, my handsome boyfriend is the top dog in school, my funtobewith friends love me, and my background is topnotch. My life is perfect. But wait, did I just hit someone?! No, no I didn't No one saw me, so nothing happened. My life is still perfect, or so I thought until "M" appeared claiming to be a witness. You think I'll let you ruin my perfect life?! Just wait until I find you!

title: Introverted Us
author: NA
synopsis: Do you ever wonder what the most popular boy at school is really like? As it turns out, he might be just as awkward and shy as any of us. That what wallflower Jayu Nam begins to discover after a chance encounter with Jahyeok Yeo, a boy in her class who seems to excel at everything in life. Well, almost. Underneath Jahyeok persona is a secret superintrovert who would rather just stay home, except his charming good looks keep forcing him into social situations. Together, Jayu and Jahyeok begin to learn a little something about friendship and maybe more

title: Pieces of Humans
author: IRON Shin,SICK
synopsis: Healed Zombies,those with rotting bodies but sound minds, are desperate for living humans; not just to kill but to receive transplants of their healthy body parts and survive! Fragmented spirits, fragmented bodies, and fragmented humanity this is the desperate survival of broken people, left only with pieces of humans!

title: Return of the Runebound Professor
author: Laurel Pursuit,Actus,AETHON,Daniel Krauss
synopsis: Magus Vermil was a scumbag the most hated professor at a magic academy. Then someone murdered him. He never would have been heard from again if not for a lost soul from Earth by the name of Noah Vines.Transmigrated into Vermil body, Noah assumes the man runic powers and extensive list of enemies. There just one problem. Noah has to teach class tomorrow, and he has no damn idea what magic is.

title: My Best Friend is an Eldritch Horror
author: Actus,AETHON,Blacklapiz Studio,Soranokami,Tevagah,Sauerkraut,Laurel Pursuit
synopsis: Good things come to those who wait. Damien Vale didn't, and now he's bound to an Eldritch creature from beyond the farthest reaches of the universe. It's unfathomable, utterly evil, and likes to be called Henry. To Damien, none of that mattered. He was going to learn magic, and he'd be damned if he let something as small as this set him back.

title: Snow and Briar
author: M. Nires
synopsis: Prince Snow is the fairest in the land, so how can they expect him to get married when nobody even comes close to his perfection? Perfect manners, perfect hair, perfectly getting everything he wants. The only thing he can't have is a life without his evil stepmother, who desperately wants him out of her hair forever. A quick scheme and three month carriage ride later, and Snow finds himself being married off to the towering Princess Briar. Is she just infatuated with him like everyone else, or does she have secrets of her own?

title: Mindful Love
author: Necole Bee
synopsis: Somewhere deep in a human brain, maybe even your own brain: Anxious and Sorrow unexpectedly fall in love, and the BrainWorld has a whole new dilemma.

title: Red Spine
author: Zeroci
synopsis: Monsters live among us.A mysterious creature called the "GENDERUWO" was just a local myth no one paid attention, no one cared until the day of the breakout. A defense force was formed to protect the people from monster attacks, and among them was Venix a young soldier discredited by the rest but desperate to prove himself. Little do they know there is more about this kid than they first believed. A Monster lives among them.

title: Forged in Flames: The Piece Maker
author: Mozza,SSUNG
synopsis: It red, hot, and burning with flames!Sage is a young boy from a small village who dreams of becoming a renowned Piece Maker like Edmond Dantes. But when his antics to help others with crafting skills get him in trouble with the local mercenary gang, a trio of rowdy blacksmiths who call themselves the Red Pepper Guild show up and come to his aid.He joins the Red Pepper Guild in their quest to solve the mystery of strange dungeons and mana stones, but can he survive the battles and the blazing dishes his eccentric guild master cooks up?

title: Sellswords & Sorcery
author: CME_T
synopsis: Honor, Bravery, Glory. Captain Ronja and her merry band of misfit mercenaries don't really know what those words mean. They just REALLY need to get paid and don't mind killing for it.

title: Disaster is Always By My Side
author: Lee Hye
synopsis: Everything seems perfect in Dami Yun's life. Her career prospects look bright, and her childhood crush Howon even moved back to Korea to confess to her. But her world turns upside down when an anonymous letter leads her to a mysterious house, where she ends up trapped for three hours except in the outside world, a decade has passed and Dami has been declared dead! Can Jaenan, the mysterious, surly god and owner of the home, help her navigate this chaos? Why does disaster strike wherever she goes? And why is this unhelpful god having prophetic dreams about them being together?!

title: Even When Im Dead
author: BestFriend,MIKA,Han Yoon seol
synopsis: On the day of my wedding, I found out that my lover was cheating on me with my best friend. I died because of their betrayal, and when I opened my eyes again, I returned to the past. I thought this was a blessing from God, a chance to take revenge. But this return was neverending as I kept dying either from their betrayal or in an accident. After my repeated death, I realized that accidents did not cause all of my deaths but that I was being murdered. So this time, I faked my death and left everything behind to catch the murderer, who was killing me repeatedly and to take my revenge finally.

title: Regression of the Close Combat Mage
author: Mayumi Sou,Mugi Ayumu,Momonome Memeno,Fuyuki23
synopsis: When Vidrak the Death God invades and the fate of humanity hangs in the balance, the greatest mages of the realm stand in defiance only to find that their spells have no effect, as the dark overlord effortlessly picks apart their attacks. Overwhelmed by a horde of monsters, longrange mage Setsuna Cromwell uses his last resort, the Amulet of Resurgence, to travel 10 years into the past. Now a freshman twice over, Setsuna must go against the grain by studying melee magic, known as the least prestigious domain and the only one with a chance of defeating Vidrak.

title: Dead Mansion
author: SGT,PTJ COMICS,Haetae,Hoin
synopsis: Childrenpure, innocent, and ready for a new beginning with their foster parents. But here at the Dead Mansion, those seemingly innocent features become lethal assets.Our orphans are schooled under the finest instructors, ensuring they meet your highest expectations and are sure to impress.However, these guardian angels come with a steep price tag. Perfection, after all, is a cruel mistress.Would you like to see the catalog now?

title: The Perfect Contract
author: TTUSOL,TAEZA,Kim Sohee
synopsis: Junwon, a perfect man, and Jui, a woman who knows her abilities and charms, strike an unusual deal: they will date with one strict condition no falling in love. What starts as a simple arrangement soon becomes complicated as unexpected feelings begin to surface. Can they stick to their promise, or will emotions get the better of them? Dive into a world where love is both the goal and the enemy, and find out if their hearts will follow the rules or break free.

title: To Drown In You
author: Jaengnwo,Sung sil
synopsis: Hyeseong, a boy living on a remote island, and Yunhae, a mysterious mermaid, become each other only friend. But soon after they meet, theyre separated after Hyeseong moves away. Six years later, Yunhae develops a mysterious power and finds Hyeseong again. Unfortunately, too much has changed, and Hyeseong can no longer dedicate all his time to her as he did in their childhood. He tells her they are too different, but Yunhae attachment to Hyeseong slowly transforms into an obsession

title: The Genius Murim Fitness Trainer
author: MIDNIGHT STUDIO,Koul,cru cru
synopsis: Ganghyeok is ruined. His gym business is failing and there's no way he can pay off his debts. But one night, while reading his favorite author's latest webnovel, he gets sucked into a world of martial arts fantasy and wakes up as a child monk in the Shaolin temple. There, he must apply his knowledge of modern fitness to survive their strict training, juggle the friends and enemies he makes along the way, and find a way to get back home.

title: In Between
author: HBCUL8ER
synopsis: Eunseo Lee and Sihwa Kang have been friends all their lives. One day, Eunseo shatters their comfortable relationship by asking Sihwa out, and Sihwa moves away soon afterward. Eunseo tries her best to forget him until they meet in a college class six years later. He seems to know about her unrequited love for him, and to make matters worse, he moves in with her family after running away from his hostile home environment. Can Eunseo cope with his sudden reappearance in her life? And is it possible that Sihwa loves her back?

title: Behind Her Highness Smile
author: Studio wooridle,Amid
synopsis: When the king offers Aerik Cladinae his own sister's hand in marriage for his meritorious deeds in battle, he didn't expect to get saddled with a limping, drooling woman like Miesa Esquillre. Driven insane by her brother's physical and psychological torture, Miesa rolls around on the ground, spills food all over herself, and screams unintelligebly as a way of communicating. But sometimes, Aerik catches a flash of shrewd understanding behind those vacant eyes. Is Miesa truly as mad as everyone thinks or is she hiding something?

title: Trapped in a Soap Opera
author: Ganno,Apricot.K
synopsis: After a life of hardship as an orphan, Jia Han finally achieves the dream of homeownership only to have her moment of jubilation cruelly cut short. While indulging in her guilty pleasurea riveting soap operashe experiences a sudden, piercing chest pain and meets an untimely demise. But when she wakes up, she finds herself not in the afterlife, but within the very drama she was watching and as none other than its villainess! In a realm where a glance sparks a scandal and a step triggers a landmine of emotions, what fate lies ahead for Jia?

title: You Can Kill Me: The Secret Bride of the Black Wolf
author: HAEMIN,Kingkang,Yim Hye
synopsis: Yeonwu Chae, a talented yet lonely composer from Korea, finds herself and her family trapped in the underworld after a car crash. In her first life, she marries Hyojo, who ultimately kills her. In her second life, she takes revenge by taking her own life in front of him. But despite her desperate wish for an end, she given another chance at life. However, this time, instead of encountering Hyojo, she is discovered by Hwita, a mysterious man with a black wolf as his guardian spirit. Can Yeonwu break the cycle and find true safety in this treacherous underworld?

title: My Stepdaughter is a Bunny
author: Karin Park,Sisse
synopsis: Gloria wakes to find that she has become the infamous evil stepmother of a cute little werebunny?! She has mysteriously entered a fantastical world of knights and werebeasts, but not as its main character. Now, she must prove that she is not the terrible person everyone thinks she is. It won be easy, but she has help. The World Tree butterfly guardians will aid her in winning the trust of her new husband and stepdaughter.

title: The Last Passage
author: RD,KIRO
synopsis: Hell? Far from it. After all, isn't this what you wanted?After choosing to end his own life, Huiseo Yun awakens adrift on a wooden raft in a bleak, desolate ocean. Attacked by a monstrous creature that defies reality, he questions if it's a dream but his instincts scream otherwise. Just when all seems lost, he is rescued by a mysterious woman who resembles a grim reaper. As he catches his breath, Huiseo asks: am I in hell?

title: Our Night Shift
author: Circlecircle,Showbi,liveby
synopsis: Miss Shin, please work your night shift at my house from now on.The workaholic vice president Jehu asks his secretary Yuna Shin four days after their company bans the night shift. Just like that, the two of them begin working together at night, but it doesn take long before their attention turns toward each other instead of work.

title: Guardian Girl
author: MJ Kim
synopsis: An immortal highschool student, Soyeong is secretly crushing on human golden retriever Huijae. Mysteriously, he keeps coming into neardeath danger and Soyeong repeatedly sacrifices herself to protect him. Something begins to grow between the two, and someone doesn't like that. What will happen to their lives and fate?!

title: Skool of Street
author: Slanket
synopsis: DJ, drop the beat! When 18yearold Kpop stan Suhyeon gets his heart broken, he turns to his actual true love, girl group sensation MainTainAespecially his bias, the group main dancer, Hailey. Leaving his bittersweet first relationship behind to transfer to Seoul, Suhyeon finds not only a spitting image of his bias in the school dance club member Hyeeun, who is supposedly Hailey younger sister, but also a new love in the most unexpected of places: the art of street dance! While helping Hyeeun overcome her stage fright, Suhyeon finds there may be more to life than love!

title: Reincarnated Murim Lord
author: JP,bookyoum,pttValley,Y.H.JANG
synopsis: Regret is the bane of old men. When aging Alliance Lord Hajin Cheon of the Grand Martial Alliance reflects on his immense legacy, he finds that he recalls little of his deeds or even the lives of his closest advisors. Stricken by a mysterious ailment, Hajin suddenly passes away only to wake up in the body of Ridan Byeok, heir to the Byeok Clan of swordsmen. The only problem is, Ridan is a wellknown wastrel, the polar opposite of the virtuous and stern Hajin. Righting the wrongs of his predecessor, Hajin begins to uncover the truth behind his death

title: When the Mad Emperor Holds Me
author: Flowermeat,Rata,Yim Hye
synopsis: Princess Celeste has endured a life of torment under her halfbrother Raf's oppressive rule. Just as she loses all hope, an unexpected opportunity for marriage appears. Batizo, the fierce emperor of the Kelenev Empire, and his enigmatic aide, Terkan, enter her life, offering a chance to escape. As Celeste finds herself caught between Batizo's wild intensity and Terkan's dark allure, a complex web of romance, jealousy, and power begins to unfold. Will Celeste navigate her way to freedom and love, or will she be ensnared by the dangerous passions that surround her?

title: BOSS RETURN
author: Seijun Yang
synopsis: The boss has returned?!Ganghun Baek, the boss of a national criminal organization, suddenly wakes up in his old high school classroom after being stabbed by his trusted subordinate.Will he be able to avoid a life of violence this time and prevent his wife's death?

title: The Holy Emperor Grandson is a Necromancer
author: Kimoong,Shadow Man,Kimdanwon
synopsis: After a neardeath experience, something has changed about the Holy Emperor troublemaker of a grandson. To be precise, his body was taken over by a Korean man who died while playing a VR video game! But when his necromancer character is mixed with a Holy Prince blood, things start getting funky. The zombies he makes are incredibly nice, his curses start healing people, and the girl he saved from being turned into a zombie suddenly gains super strength. Now he has to play the hero, but hed really rather just go for a nap.

title: The Returner Road to Retirement
author: SEOHUI,INSA,Ganjjajang
synopsis: After two decades of battling extradimensional monsters and protecting the world, Daein Lim is finally ready to retire and enjoy a peaceful life. However, the morning after his retirement party, he wakes up to find himself back in time before he even gained his powers. Armed with knowledge of the future, Daein is determined to secure his fortune and retire again, but this time within three years.

title: Overtime Elite
author: Brandon Chen,Laurel Pursuit,Inuupen,Overtime
synopsis: Omari dream was always to become a professional basketball player. But that dream was quickly crushed by reality. There school, money, his strict aunt, and the future, of which he wasn sure of until a mysterious scout discovers his talent with a ball and offers him a ticket to Overtime Elite Academy, a hightech program designed to craft the world's greatest basketball player. Does Omari have what it takes to survive against the most competitive basketball talent? Or will his dream slip away again?

title: SHIRAI
author: Andrian Januar Adilia
synopsis: Amakusa Rin, fearsome daughter of the Blue Dragon faction leader, and Horii Shinsuke, softspoken fighter of the Shirai faction, find themselves in a strange situation. To consolidate power between their factions they have to get married?! With Rin hellbent on avenging her mother death and Shin determined to marry only for love, their union is doomed from the start. After negotiating an engagement period, Rin and Shin must find a way to annul their marriage without instigating all out war between their factions. Can they succeed before their wedding night or before they catch feelings?

title: Glacias
author: Yaruno,Nawa
synopsis: Dragons don't seem scary when you've been raised by one, but how do you convince the rest of the world their fear is misplaced? Determined to create a city where humans and dragons can live together, Juka sets out with his dragon Lyth to challenge traditions and history itself. Can the everlasting hatred between two kinds be broken by a single boy and his dragon?

title: The Dang Clan Swordmaster Heir Just Wants a Normal Life
author: Hwagye,SUPJA,PSG
synopsis: The Dang clan of Sacheon, once renowned for its poison and hidden weapons, is now on the path to its demise.That is, until Yeonmyeung Dang, an outcast boy of the clan, awakens by recollecting the memories of his past lifeas the 'god of swords' who devoted his life to mastering the sword.Will the boy be able to protect his family and fulfill his dream of living a normal life?

title: The Password Is 002!
author: PADO
synopsis: The night before Sujeong plans to confess her feelings for Dojin, she runs into him on the street and is devastated to find out that he doesn't even know her name. Too afraid to face him in class the next day, Sujeong hides in the storage locker, where she meets Dojin's younger brother Jaeyun. With Jaeyun's help, will she able to win Dojin's heart?

title: The New Hire is the Demon Lord
author: HAUNI,Soobni
synopsis: Dullahan, the demon lord who once terrorized the world, finally revives in modernday Korea, eager to take revenge against the hero who defeated her centuries ago. But all she can find is his descendant, Yongrae Kim: a hapless, incompetent office worker with no prospects and no joy in life. Ending his life now would only be doing him a favor, so Dullahan decides to improve his life first but Yongrae's twotiming girlfriend and his many strict superiors at work stand in the way. Can Dullahan crush the office hierarchy and awaken Yongrae's dormant hero abilities to make her revenge more satisfying?

title: Hidden Class Gravity User
author: Nekoko,Chikuwa
synopsis: Who needs a bandit, anyway?That the last thing Ikoma Ichinose, a banditclass hunter, heard before he got kicked out of his party and ran into a monster that would kill him.But he was given a second chance at life in the form of a timeturning pocket watch.Yeah, who needs a bandit?This time, Ikoma chooses to be a gravity master to have a shot at becoming the greatest hunter of all time.

title: Surviving the Apocalypse
author: SONG
synopsis: When the apocalypse comes, the world will be ridden with bloodshed and screams of anguish. In the end, none but ashes will remain.He has been locked up in an underground prison his whole life. He does not know his name. He does not know when the world will end, nor if the world really even will end. The only thing he knows is that he has been imprisoned by his own father.

title: One Husband Is Enough
author: Go Sun Young
synopsis: A girl who has been alone her whole life stumbles upon a VR fantasy dating simulator that allows her to be who she always wanted to be someone loved by everyone. She chooses a character named Crocetta Gaetani, who grew up neglected by others just like her. Now she stuck permanently in the video game world until she can win over one of the game male leads and beat the game. Will Crocetta be able to marry one of the male leads and finally return to her reality, or will she be stuck in this VR nightmare forever?

title: I Am the Strongest Transcendent
author: Eto Shunji,Tsuchida Kenta
synopsis: You know how they say never meet your heroes? Well, what if youre literally about to die? Failed hunter Minato spent his entire life dreaming of becoming just like the 106 Progenitors, a heroic band of transcendents who defeated the Tower of Monsters three centuries ago, but he never expected to meet them in his dying moments when his highschool bully tries to kill and scapegoat him for looting their tomb. The Progenitors offer him a second lease on life by letting one of them take over his body, but that not enough for Minato: he wants them all!

title: The Ki Sisters
author: bumbae
synopsis: In the shadowy heart of Seoul near Cheonggyecheon Stream lies a sinister mansion whose porch only fools would dare tread. Welcome to the house of the Ki sisters: Jangnyeo, Salgyo, Jaerim, and Jenny. Homeschooled and raised in isolation, the four sisters and their inadvertently menacing demeanor may strike terror into the fainthearted, but don judge a book by its cover: the youngest, Jenny Ki, is a scary I mean, starryeyed hopeless romantic who out to find love! The problem is everything she knows about love is from romance novels. Will Jenny put the Ki in kiss or kill?

title: Peaceful Camping Life in Another World
author: Irinbun,MKk,GEUMUIHAENG
synopsis: Star chef Ganghyeon Lee, who has lost his sense of taste, retreats to a peaceful countryside to escape the public eye. In his grandfather's rural home, he stumbles upon a portal to another world. Taking advantage of his escape, he decides to enjoy a relaxed camping life in this new world. However, the inhabitants of this world keep showing interest in him. Will Ganghyeon be able to live a peaceful life?

title: Emerald Midnight's Lover
author: Baeck Jack
synopsis: The year is 1887 in the rolling hills of the French countryside. The estate of Viscount de Rougemerle gently basks in its verdant glory, a beacon in the twilight years of the aristocracy. With the return of the viscount wayward son Cameron, however, the tranquility of this stately home threatens to shatter into scandal. It falls upon Edgar OGrady, an Irish butler in service of the Rougemerles, to maintain decorum in the household, all the while protecting his childhood friend June and his master daughter Lady Victoria, as each furtive glance gleams the emerald green of envy

title: The Knight Only Lives Today
author: SOULPUNG,IAN,Lee Hyun Min,Kanara
synopsis: Is dying repeatedly a blessing? Enkrid's lifelong dream of becoming a knight looked to be forever out of reach, until one day he died and woke up at the beginning of that same day! Now that he has unlimited chances to train and engage in mortal combat, just how far can he go?

title: Dark Mermaid
author: DDOGAK
synopsis: She just wants to start fresh so she can graduate in peace. She just wants to leave behind all the bad memories her sleepwalking, the trauma from being bullied at school all of it. She did everything she could to keep to herself, but the class president, Haeon, just won't leave her alone. One day, when Seulbi visits the local lake Haeon recommended, she comes across something she never imagined seeing in her wildest dreams: a wild, dark mermaid.This series contains themes regarding bullying that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Press Play, Sami
author: kang eun young
synopsis: After her parents died, Sami gave up her life of fortune to live independently, doing odd jobs to make ends meet. When she starts to get involved with two of the most popular boys at her high school, Sami faces twists and turns Chan is her neighbor, and Pyojun makes her have conflicted feelings. Things get more complicated when she finds out that Chan has feelings for Pyojun as well! With her mom only keepsake in hand to keep her feet on the ground, Sami navigates obstacles that she wasn prepared for and aren even in her budget!

title: Reincarnated as My Husband Mistress
author: Tuttori,myuu,WOOJOO
synopsis: Adrienne Trovica, the sole Grand Duchess of the Rhonta Empire, suddenly dies from a seizure and wakes up in the body of Countess Bleiah Acacia, who looks exactly like her. As it turns out, Bleiah is no ordinary woman. She was the mistress of Adrienne loving husband, Noevian Trovica. Adrienne, shocked by the news, attends her funeral as Bleiah to confirm the rumor. To her surprise, she sees a man crying for her at her grave. Who is this mystery man, and was everything that she knew about her husband a lie?

title: The Superhuman Era
author: Supp
synopsis: When the xenoterran invasion began, the only ones who stood between us and the monstrous creatures were the superhumans. But while some chose to use this power for good, others had more sinister intentions.Kang Lim is a high school student with a secret he the vigilante superhero known as the White Cap, fighting back the mysterious monsters whenever he can.But the world he protects isn what it seems there is more to the emergence of the xenoterran than meets the eye, and strange forces are at play in the shadows

title: The Gwichon Village Mystery
author: Daehan LEE,YELLOW_SHEEP
synopsis: Mumyeong Heo grandmother passed away years ago.But when he visits her home to spend some time in the quiet countryside, he notices that someone kept it clean all this time.His new neighbors aren exactly thrilled by his visit. In fact, most of them don want him around.But that when his nasty neighbors go missing one by one for better or worse.

title: The Bad Son
author: Jeong Chan
synopsis: Blood ties bind, but vengeance severs, and in the heart of a heartless man, a fire ignites.Pildu Kang, a prosecutor born into a legacy of corruption, uncovers his family's harrowing involvement in his mother murder. Now, a chilling vendetta awakens the monster within, drawing out the primordial urge he has long sought to contain.Will he rely on the law to be his ally on this treacherous path, or will he become the judge, jury, and executioner?

title: Paw-ther Knows Best
author: MiTi,Gaecho
synopsis: On his daughter wedding day, a father dies and mysteriously reincarnates as the family dog in her new home. As he adjusts to his canine form, he uncovers a shocking secret: his seemingly perfect soninlaw might be unfaithful. With keen senses and newfound determination, this papa dog must protect his daughter from betrayal. Can he save her from heartache without revealing his true identity?

title: Childhood Friend Complex
author: EUNHI
synopsis: Haneul and Mincheol have been childhood friends for all of their lives, but their relationship takes on a whole new dynamic when they undergo a series of unexpected events. Although they vowed that they'd never be romantically attracted to each other, they just might be proven wrong especially when things start to escalate and neither can predict where they'll end up.

title: Zombie Funeral Services
author: Zephygaru,Mo.I
synopsis: Amidst a zombie apocalypse, Vin Yeom, an exterminator, finds a new purpose as an undertaker, specializing in funerals for the infected. Within the walls of the quarantine zone, he and his team navigate a treacherous world, providing solace to grieving families. Their company offers a unique but costly service that bridges the gap between life and death, allowing for one last goodbye. But in this world of death and despair, secrets linger, and the very loss that led Vin down this path may unearth a conspiracy that will shock the world and perhaps help him find his way back.

title: A Child Who Looks Like Me
author: FLADA,PATNOC
synopsis: A surprise pregnancy sends Jeongo, a college junior, into a panic. Her supportive boyfriend Jiheon plans a loving proposal, but a car accident erases his recent memories, including their romance. Seven years later, they reunite unexpectedly but Jiheon has no recollection of Jeongo or the fact that they share a precious daughter between them.

title: Just Roommates
author: Scragony
synopsis: They're roommates.

title: The Mushroom Girl
author: fiosketches
synopsis: As the heir to the biggest tech company in the world, Darian has it all: fame, fortune and a gorgeous girlfriend. Still, the thing he yearns the most is the one he doesn have: happiness. Will that change when he gets the chance to help Amy, the mysterious girl that lives in the forest? A magic story about love, loss and finding a place to belong.

title: Do You Like Tomboys?
author: LummyPix
synopsis: Shaye has always had a very noble dream: to date an extremely hot girl. However, after she meets her dream girl, the cute tomboy Charlie, it proves to be more difficult than expected Join Shaye and Charlie on their cute, goofy, awkward, and (hopefully?) sexy attempt at dating.

title: Miracle Simulator
author: misersdream
synopsis: Felix meant to buy a video game but ended up simulating a universe. A story about learning to love, the meaning of life, and the value of existence. Content Warning: This series may trigger derealization/unreality.

title: The Try Guys: Souper Sick
author: The Try Guys,Shen,Valery
synopsis: The Try Guys are visiting WEBTOON HQ to create their own webcomic. Except there's one problem: Zach, the ultimate comic fan, is sick! Will Keith, Kwesi, and Jonny be able to make the comic without their fearless leader? Follow them as they embrace the creative process and embark on other adventures along the way.

title: Spectral Bonds
author: JhogerSketch
synopsis: On a continent where specters and magic are but legends, Miranda, a medium with the ability to communicate with spirits, and Victor, a foreign exorcist with a mysterious past, embark on an odyssey through South America to La Gran Argentina. Bound together by their talents, they seek personal goals that only together they can accomplish. However, unaware that they are being haunted by Victor's past, their journey becomes a race against time. And what began as a simple alliance turns into something much deeper.

title: Icy Copper
author: Toivoshi
synopsis: All inhabitants of the Land of the Sun develop the power to shapeshift by the age of five all except one. Still waiting for his powers even as a teenager, Copper spends every day searching for ways to awaken his abilities. But when his search leaves him stuck in a foreign, snowcovered land, he'll come to find that the world, and his destiny, are much bigger than he could have ever imagined.

title: Selfish Romance
author: Gyogyo Park
synopsis: Hyeondo and Yumin, an ordinary man and woman in their 30s, break up with their respective partners for different reasons despite still being in love with them. Selfishly hoping to get their old flames back, the two form a plan. They pretend to date each other in hopes of provoking their former lovers. Will their selfish and foolish plan really work?

title: Escaping the Illusion
author: Poppy,Soohee
synopsis: Beloved idol Yoonjae Ahn, renowned for his impeccable charm and striking appearance, secures a coveted spot on a popular variety show, boosting his solo career. Just as he savoring success, his forgotten past resurfaces, threatening his celebrity status. Can Yoonjae shield his career from the looming secrets? With stakes at their highest, will his charm and unwavering determination prove sufficient to conquer the ghosts of his past?

title: Hell Paradise: Jigokuraku
author: Yuji Kaku
synopsis: Gabimaru, once renowned as the most powerful ninja, finds himself captured after attempting to flee his village. Yamada Asaemon Sagiri, his executioner, offers him a deal: to be exonerated of all crimes by the Shogunate, he must locate the Elixir of Life in Shinsenkyo, a realm rumored to be paradise. The man who claims to be devoid of all human emotions and attachments must now embark on a journey to explore the meaning of life, death, and humanity!!

title: Stealing Her Place
author: SERAVIEE,2L
synopsis: Yeseul arrival at her new school is anything but perfect. Not only does she make a terrible first impression, but she immediately becomes a target for bullying when the most popular girl in school, Sohui, notices their strikingly similar appearance. Despite being bullied and harassed every single day, Yeseul is determined not to back down. She knows that she just as attractive as Sohui and that itll be a breeze to steal everything from her.This series contains themes regarding bullying and abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Triple Ace
author: PAA Prado
synopsis: The top student is a fake!?Alejandro Mamani has the best grades in school but it all thanks to his perfect cheating skills. His whole charade falls apart on the day of the university selection exams, where he answers blank. Unexpectedly, on the day of the results, he wakes up with the surprise of a perfect score that hasn been seen for more than 10 years, awarding him the title of the Triple Ace.However, there is a professor assistant who knows his secret and won let him get away with his lie.

title: Return of the Hound
author: Studio W,Acro
synopsis: After being brainwashed by the emperor, Yahn has served him as his loyal puppet. Upon finding out that he has been played by the emperor, Yahn vows vengeance, but he falls to the mighty emperor powers. However, instead of dying, Yahn opens his eyes to find that he has gone back in time, to when he used to be a soldier in training. Will he now seek vengeance on the emperor, or will he go look for his family? The choice is now in his hands.

title: I'll Give You the Most Rotten One
author: Yoonda
synopsis: Ten years of relationship go down the drain when Haeru discovers that her loving boyfriend, Seo, spent the night with another woman. What begins as a series of small misunderstandings snowballs into something much bigger as the college sweethearts wade through love, temptation, and workplace drama. Well, what better way to get back at her cheating boyfriend than to take the most rotten revenge ever?

title: The Cup of Vengeance Is in Your Hands
author: JIBSA,tado,SCAMPER
synopsis: Princess Eudith story begins when her cruel brother, the king, sells her off to the neighboring kingdom to marry the queen powerless stepson, Prince Franz. Eudith becomes a pawn in the queen plot to discredit Franz and place her biological son, Krald, on the throne.Desperate, Eudith attempts to end her misery but wakes up on the day of her fateful journey. Armed with knowledge and experience from her past life, Eudith seizes the chance for revenge by helping Prince Franz take his rightful place on the throne. Will Eudith succeed in her revenge and find happiness?

title: Powerless
author: chikinmu,DBoom
synopsis: It time! Introducing, in the powerless corner, the former undisputed MMA champion Gwangho Hwang, with a professional record of 49:1 and a reputation for all kinds of dirty tactics, returning fresh from a supposed permanent suspension. And in the powered corner well, folks, let just say it a murderer row of deadly opponents with an array of special abilities. Welcome to the octagon, the ultimate showdown between a league of enhanced superfighters going up against Gwangho brawn and his manager Seyeon brains! The bell rings for Round 1. Touch gloves, and face the pain! Here we go!

title: Nebula's Civilization
author: Wirae,Beomgwin
synopsis: Seongun Choi is the topranked player in the game Lost World,being the only player to have completed all its achievements. However, his triumph is shortlived as a mysterious message transports him to the real Lost World,transforming him from a mere gamer to a contender for godhood. Amidst others vying for divinity, will Seongun be able to achieve true godhood and reign supreme in this new realm?

title: Monster Princess of the Snowy Mountain
author: Lee Nakeum,seewater,suho
synopsis: Valerie Beloff, a princess in exile, decides to take her own life on her 19th birthday. Abused by her own mother and exiled for her mother crimes, she had to live in the freezing Makleroad palace by herself, and she somehow acquired the powers of an ancient monster the power to freeze things. Hopeless, she seeks an escape in death only to find herself before her cruel mother, yelling at her once again. Is she dead? Is she reliving a memory? When her mother strikes her, the throbbing pain lets her know that this is neither a dream nor a memory!This series contains themes regarding child abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: The Worst Villainess
author: LICO,Shidaka Saya
synopsis: Possessing a character in a fictional story is one thing, but possessing a character in your own story is another especially when youve become a dramatic villainess in a typical Kdrama series. The only way Miso can escape from this world is to live through all of the episodes, but she has to deal with cliche tropes such as an arranged marriage with the male lead and an unnecessary rivalry with the female lead. Will Miso be able to break away from this predetermined destiny and find another happy ending for all of her characters?

title: Myst, Might, Mayhem
author: Madbird,Kim Tae Hyung,HANJUNG WOLYA
synopsis: All Jeong wants is a second chance for revenge! His grandfather gruesome death has transformed him into the bloodthirsty and ruthless Scythe Demon. He will stop at nothing until he has killed the man responsible. Yet rage and determination alone are not enough. He must train in martial arts if he ever wants to stand a chance against such a formidable foe. Will he succeed in his revenge on the murderer of his grandfather?

title: The Demon King's Warrior Daughter
author: Geobong Choi,Ppangbaksa,Jumeok
synopsis: Nobody said being a parent was easy. It especially hard for Belphegor Verscios, the adoptive father of an exceptionally gifted human girl who insists on becoming a warrior someday and defeating the Demon King who, unbeknownst to her, happens to be him. But when youre a doting father like Belphegor, what else can you do but try to support her dreams while simultaneously making sure she never reaches her goal? It a fine line to walk, but he must succeed at any cost, or suffer the worst fate he could ever imagine disappointing his daughter.

title: My Virtual God is a Teenage Girl
author: Park Jang Go,Yi Woo
synopsis: From good looks, brains, hot body, wealth, and a gorgeous family. It seemed like Jumin life was god perfect. Until he realized that his world was merely a simulation controlled by well, a teenage girl! With just a click of her mouse, Jumin loses everything and returns to high school! Will he break free from the program and reclaim what he lost?

title: The Video Game Store Under the Barbershop
author: Ilkwon Ha
synopsis: High school freshman Miso is enthralled when she sees her classmate Hyojeong playing a retro handheld video game on the train. Hyojeong always seemed kind of intimidating, but the way her eyes sparkle as she plays makes Miso want to learn more about retro games, and muster up the courage to befriend her.When Miso and her older brother Minjun head to the old video game store in their town, not only do they find that it's run by Hyojeong and her older sister, they also discover a nostalgic portal to the past

title: I Didn Sign Up to be a Nanny!
author: Eun You,Kong Ja,Honey Bambi
synopsis: While working the regular shift in a supermarket, Ailene finds herself waking up in the body of a nanny within a fantasy novel. Knowing this character dies at the hands of the twin princes at the beginning of the novel, Ailene vows to raise these boys to be kindhearted and avoid their dark storyline. She fits right into her role and things seem to be looking up until the empire mad dog Duke Kasar stumbles into her life and asks her to pretend to be his lover. Will Ailene make it through the fantasy novel alive?!

title: How to Hold His Leash
author: 99C,BECKDO
synopsis: Not a single day has passed by without Yeonu calling her verbally abusive boss Junhu Kang a son of a b****. After being cursed out for the millionth time, Junhu turns into an actual dog. What's worse is that Yeonu becomes Junhu's owner, and the only way for him to temporarily turn back into a human is if she touches him. After internally cursing him 317,920 times, Yeonu finally gains the upper hand against her supercilious CEO, who is now an adorable white puppy.

title: Star Catcher
author: Rotaniah
synopsis: After battling with numerous hardships and an unsuccessful attempt at his own life, Lucas transformed from a true ray of sunshine to a meek and depressed young adult. He shuts out those around him to focus on his studies at the worldrenowned Star Valley University in the hopes of making a positive impact in the world one day. Never would he imagine that a bychance run in with a stranger would result in him learning to forgive and love himself, and find the passion to live life for himself again.

title: Unnie, I Like You!
author: Jeongussi
synopsis: Park Chanmi vividly remembers her past life, where she harbored deep feelings for the beautiful Hanbyeol, whose life tragically ended too soon. In her present life, Chanmi is startled to discover that her lost love has returned as a university professor yet does not recall their past life. Fearing history may repeat itself, Chanmi is determined to protect the sole person she cherishes the most.

title: Weeb vs. Jock
author: Merryweather
synopsis: A popular girl meets a strange guy in detention.

title: Replaced
author: NICO
synopsis: Ten year old Ruby Ledger has been missing for over 6 months. Her family thinks they've finally found herThe truth? Well, I won't tell if you don't.

title: Candid Hearts
author: antlerella
synopsis: After a reckless electrical fire burns their dorm room to a crisp, college girls Bonnie and Aline find themselves homeless the day before their semester starts! With nothing but the clothes on their back, the mysterious richgirl Kitty Kandikova offers them an deal they can't refuse: free rent, all amenities paid, and essentially a life of luxury. The catch: they must completely give up their social lives to become her fake best friends, and potential bridesmaids?!

title: The Exiled Hero
author: Bluecliffe,GGULBEOM,minsun
synopsis: After seven grueling years, Jihan Yu, a support hero, is expelled from his guild. But fate throws him a curveball a contract with an elemental grants him the ultrarare power of a Wind Elementalist! In a world ravaged by monsters and invaders from other realms, Jihan joins the underdog Epic Guild. Can he utilize his newfound power and strategic mind to lead the ragtag guild to greatness, all while mastering his abilities, overcoming fierce rivalries, and surviving in this chaotic world?

title: To Whom It No Longer Concerns
author: LICO,fairydragon
synopsis: Exploited by her brother, betrayed by her sister, and killed by her husband. So ended the tragic story of Ariana Lopezuntil, at the moment of her death, she suddenly finds herself back in the past. Now that she has a chance to do it all over again, she enlists the help of Duke Dante Heigenberg, the most feared and desired man in the entire empire, to take revenge against her family and reclaim what rightfully hers. But strangely, the duke seems to want Ariana more than just for her extraordinary musical talent

title: The Genius Spirited Streamer
author: LICO,OPST,Midgoboneun
synopsis: Gyeongbok Lee possesses a gift that grants him a sixth sense and supernatural foresight however, this ability comes at a steep price, debilitating him each time it is used. But when Gyeongbok tries virtual reality gaming for the first time, he makes a startling discovery: not only could he leverage his psychic ability to gain a significant advantage in the virtual world, but he was also entirely free from its afflictions. Seizing this opportunity, Gyeongbok sets out to become a legendary video game streamer, turning his curse into his greatest asset.

title: Hiding Out in an Apocalypse
author: ROAD WARRIOR,Double_S,DD
synopsis: Gyu Park is a survivor who predicted and prepared for the coming apocalypse. In this ruined world, he is willing to do anything and everything he can to protect the comforts of his bomb shelter.

title: King of the Arena
author: LICO,Kyeongchan Han
synopsis: Firstyear Gilsu Lee transfers schools to run from the bullying and violence. And the new place seems almost perfect. Everyone in his class is friendly and kind, and no one is bullying anybody.Violence? No, we don do anything like that in this school. That what the Arena is for.Don forget, Gilsu. What happens in the ring stays in the ring!

title: The Extra Academy Survival Guide
author: Korita,GREEN KYRIN
synopsis: Ed Rothstaylor is a thirdrate villain in a game, disowned by his family and kicked out of the dormitory for his misdeeds. One day, our main character wakes up as this very Ed, and realizes he must earn a scholarship so he can graduate and be set for life. Now living in the woods, he resolves to keep away from the protagonists, but four of the female leads just won't leave him alone. Not only that, his presence starts to change the timeline and events of the game! Can Ed help the story progress while staying out of the limelight?

title: My Very Own Tower Strategy Guide
