author: XNAME,Sado.(REDICE STUDIO),goodluck
synopsis: 15 days until the apocalypse happens. That's what Hoyeong Lee, a 29yearold office worker, learns when he takes the mysterious medicine he got for saving a goblin from a bear trap. As it turns out, it allows him to level up more easily and provides him with a strategy guide! Everyone in the world is forced into groups to conquer the mysterious Apocalypse Tower, and Hoyeong has to find a way to work with his teammates so that everyone makes it to the top alive. Will his ability give him an advantage, or will it end up spelling out his doom?

title: Peace Restaurant
author: tyang,SeowooSeowoo
synopsis: Chef Sua, with her unrivaled culinary skills, doesn't just rule over Peace Restaurant, Seoul's most peculiar eatery she weaves harmony between cosmic enemies now seated as tablemates. The tension in her restaurant simmers not from culinary rivalry but from the precarious peace among patrons from warring dimensions. Will Sua's culinary diplomacy be enough to maintain this balance, or is her restaurant destined to become the epicenter of an ultimate showdown?

title: The Students of Illip Arts High
author: Backbone
synopsis: Meet Sol Han, the human photocopier who can replicate anything she sees with precision! One day, she stumbles upon a mysterious genius's drawing in a VR game, igniting her passion for art. Curiosity leads her from a quiet countryside to Illip Arts High School, the epitome of artistic excellence. Amidst challenges and tangled friendships, Sol's journey, a captivating tale of youthful growth and camaraderie, unfolds in the picturesque halls of Illip.

title: My Life as a Loser 2
author: PTJ COMICS,Peanut,SW Jeon
synopsis: This isn the life I wanted!!! After reliving high school as Jinu, the boy he once bullied, Ancheol is now a new person. But his new life takes an unexpected turn. Once again, he is sent back in time to live as Jinu. But this time, Jinu is also back as Ancheol!

title: Melting Slowly
author: Team SABANA,Team J,Early Flower
synopsis: Yeomin Chae has been living in the shadow of her halfsister, Nari Chae, ever since they were kids. One day, Seungjae, Yeomin's exboyfriend, tells her that he marrying Nari out of the blue. After being betrayed by the person she trusted most, she runs into Hwan Yun, who is the grandson of Taeju Group chairman. Frustrated with her life, she suggests to Hwan that he marry her. As the two decide to get married, what exciting events and struggles will they encounter?

title: A Flame Reborn
author: Saint Nine,Yang Pyung,Painkiller
synopsis: Logan MacLine, a middleaged knight fighting for the independence army, is intent on getting revenge against the empire which took over the kingdom and executed his brother when he ends up dying in battle. But when he wakes, he is a young man again, and has yet to be disowned for his terrible behavior. Using his experience and knowledge from his past life, Logan recruits a few talented individuals to develop new weapons, build an army, and make enough money to fund it all. But will he be able to make amends with his family and stop the empire's march?

title: Reflection of the Soul
author: Magovi
synopsis: Annie is a lonely girl who is afraid of mirrors, while Liam is a wellknown model and actor. It may seem unlikely that two people with such different lives could relate to each other, but sometimes, people's external appearance doesn't reflect their true souls. This is the story of two broken hearts and their journey toward selfacceptance and love.This series contains themes regarding bullying, selfharm, and mental health and may not be suitable for all readers. And if you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at crisistextline.org.

title: My Crush Got Possessed by the Duke
author: Dadam,Juksoon
synopsis: Soa knows that having a crush on a childhood friend can be complicated, but it even harder when he gets possessed by the duke?! When Soa friend Yuseong is suddenly possessed by Duke Hereis De Licariel, they must figure out a way to get Hereis back home which is easier said than done when Hereis sounds like he came straight out of a fantasy novel! Can Soa get her childhood friend back while having to juggle academics, sports, and a duke who also happens to be a swordmaster?

title: Savior of Divine Blood
author: Eto Shunji,silou,3rd Ie,Studio No.9
synopsis: Subaru is an average guya loser, in fact. Becoming a Player who enters mysterious gates and slays creatures to defend humanity is a farfetched dream. But after several years of constant bullying and abuse, a Door of Trials appears before him, and he finally becomes a Player. But his brother is out to get him, and Subaru is completely outmatched. Furthermore, the Sky Clock is ticking down, which could mean the end of the world when it hits zero. Can Subaru overcome his brother and uncover the truth behind the gates that plague the world?

title: Why I Quit Being the Demon King
author: Daeil Kim,Agra
synopsis: Demiurgos DCLXVI, or Deus, is the 666th resurrection of the Demon King, fated to battle a warrior of the Pure Blood clan every 100 years to liberate his fellow demons from hell. But instead of waiting, Deus escapes 20 years early to forge a new identity among the humans.

title: Not Interested in Dating
author: seoulso
synopsis: "I want to live a simple life." Dohui wants to live as she always has, and her coworker Dongi likes to be alone. They have no intention of dating anyone in their workplace Or do they? We invite you to the intimacy of two people who keep encountering each other.

title: My Lord was Already Into Me When I Noticed
author: Yearend,Gyosi
synopsis: Tenyearold Celine Mars dreams of becoming a great knight escort just like her father. She set to serve under Damien Willow, the heir of a powerful Duke. There only one problem he a total weakling, or so she thinks. Celine vows to train the poor, defenseless Damien to stand up for himself, completely unaware of his real strength. Meanwhile, Damien instantly takes a liking to Celine, finding her cluelessness and pure intentions both amusing and endearing. When will Celine finally realize she got the wrong idea about Damien?

title: Vampire Family
author: unfins
synopsis: As a family of vampires, the Dragomirs have long stayed hidden away from humans, but middle child Natalia longs for one thing: friends. She convinced her family to let her go to school, and has chosen her seat neighbor, Evangelo, to be her first friend. But he is not your typical student either

title: Hiding in the Moon
author: Puik
synopsis: Since she ran away from the capital, Siomara has played it safe. Mainly she tries to ignore the Darkness that inhabits this world, which she is now capable of seeing, but more importantly, she makes sure that the Darkness ignores her as well. But when a mysterious neighbor moves in that could also be like her, Siomara must decide if shell risk getting closer to him, despite all the warnings of the danger that he comes with.

title: Winter Before Spring
author: moonbun00,rinucomics
synopsis: Hana finds herself grappling with an unexpected emotion when she realizes she fallen in love with her best friend, who happens to be a girl. Fearing she'd be rejected, her best friend unexpectedly reciprocates, and they embark on a new romantic journey together. Hana is suddenly struck down, her world crashing down as cracks begin to form in what seemed to be her perfect vision of love when she is confronted with the nasty truth about her new girlfriend. But when things seem bleakest and Hana has given up on love, a new face arrives at the school that has the potential to change everything

title: The Apothecary Prince
author: kangho HA,Dadang,BK_Moon
synopsis: In a twist of fate, the life of a doctor of Korean medicine flips upside down in a single night. Doctor Han Lee is reborn as Lachiel, the sickly Crown Prince of the Empire of Magentano. Han is now armed with medical knowledge and skills found nowhere else in this new world but can he heal an empire and mend his own body at the same time? Witness his journey of selfexploration and resilience as he maps destiny's meridian, in pursuit of the acupoint that can reverse his fate.

title: Do Not Hold on to the Broken Branch
author: CAPTAIN,jocopia
synopsis: After two failed engagements and the downfall of her family, Deatrice, the Duke's daughter and once the most celebrated socialite in high society, finds herself in a reluctant reunification with Lucius. Lucius is her former fiance and currently the Emperor's favorite knight whose life had been ruined by her own father six years ago. Is this forced marriage the beginning of Lucius' vengeance? Could fate turn it into a second chance for them to get over the shadows of their painful past and find true love?

title: Wail of a Dragon Rage
author: jordan,gegegek
synopsis: Ananta, a descendant of one of the First Six Incarnates, can transform into an unstoppable brawling dragon whenever anything stands in his way. And it's a power he'll need in his quest to exact revenge against the Wings Incarnate, a powerhungry deceiver that resembles a heavenly angel only in appearance.

title: Return of the Genius Player
author: cookiyo,Asleep24Hours
synopsis: The Hunters League is a sport where only those with supernatural powers may compete, promising fame, glory, and incredible prizes. Changhyeon Lee had it all, but faces an abrupt downfall during his slump. Cast aside by even his own team, his world crumbles but fate deals him an unexpected hand when a fatal encounter with a 10ton truck ends his life, only to send him back in time to the day he discovered his powers. Armed with a second chance, Changhyeon is determined to reclaim and transcend his former glory in the Hunters League.

title: Want to See My Cat?
author: samtae
synopsis: Chayeong Mun had the perfect life a peaceful life in the countryside with a loving husband, three cats who run the house, and two dogs who think theyre cats. One day, she goes into the city to meet her friends and dies while saving a student from being hit by a truck. The god in the afterlife gives her the incredibly rare chance to go back to her wonderful life, but only under the condition of going back 10 years in time. Given the second chance, Will she be able to marry her husband again and rebuild that perfect life she knew?

title: Degree of Love
author: EuAeng
synopsis: Yejin, a smart girl from a poor family who gets into a top university, has zero dating experience. Now that she's in college, she wants to find love, so she puts herself out there, but Enter Hyeon, an elite Taekwondo athlete, her only guy friend from childhood, who masquerades as her "bestie," but is he really? Yejin is determined to support her family through academic achievement, but she also wants love. Can she have both? How will Yejin navigate the journey of having it all?

title: The Reason for the Twin Lady Disguise
author: Amamiya Ley.,MONA
synopsis: The Lowreis family was wrongly sentenced to execution for attempting to murder the royal family. As Linali Lowreis, the daughter of the family, is on the brink of death, she fervently prays for a second chance. Miraculously, she wakes up three years in the past, reuniting with her deceased family members. However, tragedy looms as her brother, Liam, is poised to attend the School of Poltis, the reason for the family's tragedy. She begs her father to send her instead of her brother, as she is better at sword fighting. Now, faced with a new identity and unexpected challenges, Linali must attend the School of Poltis in her brother's place.

title: A Demon's Wish
author: Zigozi9,Muneki
synopsis: Doya Seo, a demon, is one day captivated by a mysterious dream. That same day, he happens upon Wish So, a new freshman. Curiously, each moment their paths intersect, Doya finds himself engulfed in a perplexing whirl of emotions and physical sensations that his demonic sensibilities fail to decipher. Meanwhile, Wish finds herself amidst a flurry of events after being invited to the home of famous actor Jaehyeon Woo. In a world where the supernatural coexists with humanity, and caught between the devilish charm of Doya and Jaehyun allure, will Wish be able to navigate her school life without trouble?

title: S.K.T(Swallow Knights Tales)
author: Goodang,Hanheun,Kim ChoulGon
synopsis: Endymion passed the interview to finally become a Swallow Knight because he cute? His lifelong dream has turned out to be nothing like what he had expected. He thought knights were supposed to be honorable and tough! But there is also good news: his past experience as a party host may come in handy after all. How will his life change as he becomes a Swallow Knight?

title: Princess Hurricane
author: RD
synopsis: Taepung Gang is a transfer student with a dream. He going to become the number one fighter at his new allboys school, and he got the skills, muscle, and notoriety to make it happen. He definitely wasn supposed to swap places with Princess Lily, a peaceloving royal from a fairytale land without either of their memories! Will Lily fulfill Taepung dream of becoming the school best fighter? Will Taepung survive his new life as the cursed princess? How does a delinquent become a princess anyway, or a princess become a delinquent for that matter?

title: King Game
author: Shin Hyungwuk,killer whale
synopsis: Chomin has been violently bullied since middle school, but when his estranged brother suddenly dies in a motorcycle accident, Chomin finds out he was the leader of Imperial Gang, a huge gang. Now in possession of his brother's phone, Chomin seizes this chance to get revenge on his high school bullies by ordering his brother's underlings to beat them up. But the King Game begins when his brother's girlfriend shows up and threatens to expose him unless he cooperates in taking down a rival gang. With his life now on the line, can Chomin manage to continue this farce?

title: My Comeback as the Youngest Member
author: mattgom,Kang seoul
synopsis: After being disqualified from the famous boy group survival reality show Stardust Project, Seohan finds himself stuck in a mundane life of parttime work, unable to achieve his dreams of debuting. But then, an unexpected twist of fate catapults him eight years back in time, just before the inception of the show. Now equipped with years of experience, Seohan is determined to rewrite his story and fulfill his dreams with this second chance. With the many challenges and dark sides of the music industry, will he finally succeed in debuting as a member of a boy band this time?

title: They Wish to Take Away My Child
author: I Rui,lobster
synopsis: When Iris Locha gazes into the enchanted mirror inherited from her parents, she's met with a haunting glimpse of what lies ahead. A future where she grapples with a terminal illness, and her husband's mistress relentlessly pressures her to abandon her husband and child. Amidst the dark secrets, sinister plots, and misunderstandings, can Iris carve out her path to happiness?

title: Return of the King of Hell
author: BARUNFLOWER
synopsis: Yama, the King of Hell, chooses retirement in search of happiness, but his reincarnation is put on hold when his successor, Harry, abandons his post to pursue a mysterious goal on the human plane.With the aid of the undertakers, humans who can draw forth the power of the Underworld, Yama attempts to quell the chaos and return everything to its rightful place.Will Yama tread the cycle of rebirth without faltering, or will the echoes of his past haunt his journey? One thing for sure there will be hell to pay.

title: The Fish I Loved
author: WUJUBOMBOM,BUBAL,WOODO,HONG EUNAE
synopsis: Yana Jeong, a typical girl, runs into a strange man who out of breath during one of her parttime jobs. Little did she know that this was Kai Shim, the son of the CEO of a large jewelry corporation called Inoroo, who also happens to be a merman. Yana coincidentally runs in Kai again when she ends up working as a waitress at his birthday party, where a series of accidents lead to the two of them meeting each other again. Will Yana be able to keep up with these unexpected events happening one after another?

title: My Beloved Oppressor
author: LICO,Cersei
synopsis: When the hand that used to so lovingly hold Annette Rozenberg ends up being the one that causes the downfall of her family, Annette demands that Heiner Waldemar give her a divorce. But Heiner refuses, stating that he must see her miserable by his side, no matter what. At odds, the two continue a precarious relationship, only to be met with wounds of the past that bring them tragically together. "This series contains themes regarding abuse and selfharm that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/)."

title: Reincarnator
author: On the Rock,Sea Slater&Mudskipper,ALLA
synopsis: Abyss, an alternate reality created by a bored god, plucks humans from earth and sets them against monsters and each other in a sick gladiator game. Hansoo Kang, one of the last four survivors, is sent back in time twenty years as the last hope for humanity. He teams up with long lost school friends and enemies to relearn skills and arm himself with the knowledge to break the game once and for all.

title: Wrong Quest
author: OzzaWorld
synopsis: Adventuring isn as easy as it looks. This band of misfits are in way over their heads.

title: Wanna be Friends?
author: Giushia
synopsis: Sienna has never been great at making friends. But it a new year and a new school, and she not going to repeat the mistakes of the past! She going to make whole new mistakes as she crashes headfirst into the most popular ice king at school, Ian. The famous student keeps himself closed off from others, but Sienna unorthodox methods of making friends will give him more than one heart attackand maybea crush?

title: RE: Monarch
author: AETHON,Moonquill,J. McCoy
synopsis: A progression fantasy epic set in a timeloop where planning and cleverness are as vital as swordplay, about a spoiled prince who discovers what it means to rule. Watch as he gains power, learns magic, forges alliances, and delves deeper into the mystery of the loop itself and the nature of his relationship with the ruthless antagonist.

title: Manny
author: A.Rasen
synopsis: This series contains graphic content and themes regarding mental health, bullying, and abuse that may not be suitable for all readers.When Manny enters the Rodraguez family's life, his charming facade masks a dark nature that threatens to tear their household apart. As tensions rise and secrets are exposed, the family must confront the true identity and sinister motives of their supposed caregiver.

title: Love 4 a Walk
author: Nuria Sanguino
synopsis: Pam's heart has been broken one too many times, and being dumped over her unruly dog Bob was the last straw. Now determined to care for Bob on her own, how long can this hopeless romantic resist falling for her mysterious yet compassionate neighbor Tyler especially when he's so good with dogs?

title: K.O!
author: Sable Studio
synopsis: Seen as a problematic high school student, Joel Mora is feared by all. That is, until Emma, a shy girl from his class, decides to get to know him better. Now, Joel is in the middle of a social whirlwind, trying to find his place.

title: Divine Delivery
author: JAMGGYU,oceanlady,GGULBEOM
synopsis: Enter the world of Hajun Lee, just your average delivery guy trying to make ends meet. But when he's summoned to Olympus for a special delivery, his life takes an unexpected turn. Suddenly, he's the personal delivery man for the gods, earning big bucks and upgrading his gear with each risky delivery. Follow his daring escapades through dungeons and battles with monsters as he learns to outsmart them all. From one divine job to the next, Hajun faces it all with wit and guts. But can he keep up the hustle of being a regular delivery guy while also serving the mighty gods?

title: Can't Get Enough of You
author: VODAUVEU,QuornQuorn,FLADA
synopsis: After losing his parents in a tragic car accident at a young age, Taejun Kim vows never to forgive those responsible. Now, as an adult, fate reunites him with Soeun Han, the daughter of the driver who took his parents' lives. Young, powerful, rich, and handsome Taejun is hungry for revenge and will bully Soeun until he feels satisfied. However, complications arise when love enters the equation, blurring the line between resentment and affection. A story in the making, in which "I will never forgive them!" turns into "I think I like you".

title: The Gardener in a Hunter World
author: Tomozo,GITAE CHON,Sliber
synopsis: Jiha is living a relatively quiet life, gathering resources after raids and selling potions from his general store as a workerclass hunter. Little did he know, taking a nap on top of an ancient text would completely change his life. He is transported to a magical forest, where he gathers rare ingredients to create neverbeforeseen potions and meets mythical creatures that help him on his adventures. Soon, he starts to build up his abilities to become a skilled alchemist, and highlevel hunters start to see him in a different light. How will Jiha make use of his newly acquired skills?

title: My Naughty Deity
author: SeoAh
synopsis: The higher you climb, the harder you fall. So let just stay level.Haetsal life motto has worked so far, so good that is, until she discovers that the ancient god of lust and pleasure has moved in as her nextdoor neighbor. Although she has vowed to live a life of peace, free from all the risks and dangers of the modern world, she just might take her chances with this one.

title: My Villainous Family Won't Let Me Be
author: hatti,Mitchu,Lee huin
synopsis: A distant echo from a life longforgotten; shattered shards of an ominous future. When her late mother heirloom pendant is broken, Elodie Perdia regains the memories of Gaeul Yun, a girl from our world who realizes she landed in the body of a villainess from a fantasy novel. In the story, Elodie serves as the dark foil to the virtuous heroine and is destined for an early grave a dark fate that can perhaps be avoided with Gaeul knowledge of future events!

title: Children of Orbit
author: Na Yoonhee,GooKim
synopsis: Siblings Seong Ryu and Bin Ryu have always been in the spotlight with their good looks, magnetic charms, and diverse talents. However, Bin has a secret, which involves the quiet valedictorian Yeongin Jeong. Seong, who also secretly harbors an inferiority complex toward Bin, begins to approach Yeongin. The three characters must face their complicated family history and encounter emotions theyve never experienced before on their journey to adulthood.

title: The Genius Assassin Who Takes It All
author: Studio Sigma,MOZO
synopsis: Waking up as the main villain of his own novel was not part of the original plan. Now a lowly level 10 assassin, Ganghu Shin must use all of his prior knowledge as the author to navigate the fantasy world he created himself, and somehow alter the ending in order to return to the real world. Can he change the outcome and defeat the real villain to prevent his own demise and save this world from impending doom?

title: Supremely Talented Player
author: Horakan,SNanyc,Chena
synopsis: Six years ago, humanity was almost brought to an end when mysterious towers filled the skies across the globe, unleashing deadly monsters. Fortunately, the people known as players emerged, blessed with supernatural powers that they harnessed to save mankind. Among them is Yuseong Kang, a phenomenal player who has saved the world time after time. Once again, he has successfully averted global catastrophe and in an internationally broadcasted interview praising his heroic endeavors, he says, Im just in it for the money.

title: Office Romance from Hell
author: Nokhye,Dangcheom,Hwang DoTol
synopsis: Dumped by her boyfriend and fired from her job, Jineon, her family's breadwinner, has no time to cry over the spilled milk. She must find another job and fast. Enter The Hell, a mysterious company with great pay, excellent worklife balance, and an easy commute! What more could she ask for? Or so she thought. Little did she know, she had walked into hell literally. How will she navigate the harrowing journey in the hellscape of her new job with King Yeomra, her stunning new boss, further complicating everything? Could love blossom in this pit of hell?

title: Returned by the King
author: KIMU,SH,Ansoseoul
synopsis: In a world where one's worth is determined by how powerful their skill is, Taehyeon is 35, unawakened, and barely able to scrape by as a pack bearer for monster hunters. But when a mysterious being calling itself the King gives him a skill of his own, Taehyeon gets a second chance at life. Now he back in high school and armed with Gluttony, a skill that allows him to block and absorb the skills of others!

title: Sweetheart
author: Buttercup
synopsis: Goodlooking loner, Scott Hart is an autistic model who accidentally discovers the secret of the most feared girl at his school, Penelope Suit. And oddly enough, they get intertwined in an atypical friendship. But is friendship all there really is to it?

title: The Heavenly Demon's Descendant
author: Jung seonyul,Yuon Im
synopsis: The once upandcoming monster hunter Suho has plateaued at B Class, dashing his hopes of ever avenging his parents' deaths. Enter the ghost of the Cheonma, former divine Murim master and Suho's direct ancestor! Fortunately for Suho, the disembodied Cheonma needs a body to hunt down his arch nemesis, the Blood Demon, and Suho is the perfect fit. Will Suho strike a deal with the Cheonma to escape his rut and gain the power to finally avenge his parents?

title: Potion Witch
author: imjayu
synopsis: Vanna is an ordinary pharmacist who runs a small herb shop in Blalock City.Yet, when night falls, the mysterious Witch Raven emerges in this seemingly serene city, casting curses upon her targets before vanishing into the shroud of darkness. Consequently, Vanna often receives requests to make potions to lift the witch curse. However, her days are disrupted when a policeman approaches her, and the two ultimately form a partnership in the hopes of unveiling the truth behind Triplet Academy. Will the unlikely duo succeed in uncovering the mysteries of the Academy?

title: Fallen to Paradise
author: BY,YoonJu,Wonderdream
synopsis: Ange, the daughter of Duke Glaster, believes her life is all planned out as she is set to marry Philip Cardiner, the rightful heir to the throne. However, her plans are disrupted when Philip's brother, William Cardiner, schemes against him and removes him from the line of succession. In order to secure his power, William forces Ange to marry Aiden Fitzroy, an illegitimate child born between the emperor and a commoner. Will Ange learn to love the humble stranger she was forced to marry?

title: Plus One
author: Gloria__
synopsis: We are having a baby! From pregnancy to baby crawling, every day is filled with cuteness and no sleep.

title: Ari, San, and the Reaper
author: RBKjin
synopsis: When executioner and champion of the people, Master Yu, goes missing, Ari, San, and Reaper set out to find him, each for different reasons. San, the dokebi and Master Yu's biggest fanboy, looks to him for guidance. Ari, a mysterious child that can't speak, seeks revenge. And Reaper is on a mission to collect the Master's soul before it expires and they all face greater consequences.

title: Lorena Immaculate
author: HoratioMarissa
synopsis: Lorena Ruiz has a gift from God. Noa Asadi and Chuck Williamson run a ghosting hunting vlog channel. When both parties are called to investigate the same haunting, neither knows what to make of the other. But as the haunting begins to spiral out of control, Lorena finds it harder and harder to act like the perfect nun she was raised to be. Her new companions have questions; about her, about her socalled power, and about the mysterious Convent she belongs to. And through it all, something watches from the house's darkest corners.

title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
author: Dark Horse Comics, LLC
synopsis: After the conclusion of the Hundred Year War, Avatar Aang and his friends, Zuko, Sokka, Katara, and Toph work to heal the Four Elemental Nations and usher in a new age of progress. Follow the gang as they discover secrets of the past, battle new threats, heal old wounds and make new friends in these stories that take place between the hit animated television series Avatar: The Last Airbender and The Legend of Korra.

title: My Killer Boyfriend
author: GhostfaceNikol
synopsis: It's the Killer's job to trick his targets into falling in love with him, which hasn't been an issue in the past. That is until he ends up falling in love with his next target, who just so happens to be an infamous celebrity and someone from his past. Can a serial killer date his celebrity target? Or is that too taboo?

title: Demon Prince & The Salaryman
author: Merryweather
synopsis: A salaryman summons Astaroth, a Prince of Hell, to help him stop getting bullied at work.

title: Osora
author: ToniRenea
synopsis: Prince Osora is destined to rule over the Calaveras Kingdom in a life planned out by his family since birth, when his father presented him to the kingdom as male. However, the magicwielding race called Sergos has a different plan for Osora: to use him as collateral in war with the humans. Bound by what others force him to be and trapped in a love triangle between a promised fiancee and his childhood best friend, Osora must recreate his own story. This series contains themes regarding sexuality, gender identity, homophobia, transphobia, and other prejudices.

title: It Just Business
author: youngha,gongsa
synopsis: A love life? Give me a break.A complete nonbeliever when it comes to romance, Eunho is focused on climbing the ladder at work. Smart with excellent social skills to boot, both her bosses and clients love her. But when a new hire suddenly appears in front of her and an old first love start to shake things up again, she can help but waver.

title: CHILDREN OF VAMFIELD  by DARK MOON
author: HYBE
synopsis: Seven boys live under the care of Ms. Marge at Vamfield House. Their peaceful lives are shattered one day after they stumble upon a secret room

title: The Executioner
author: Lee Jehwan,Park Bumjin
synopsis: A hero should never kill anyone, not even the worst of villains.Gangyu could never understand why his team of heroes lived by those words, but he tried his best to do the same until the villain who wiped out his squad killed his brother in prison.Gangyu breaks his vow and enters Ruculus with permission to kill as the prison executioner. Now, he must fight his way through the villains to kill the worst of them all.

title: A Couple of Obligations
author: GULDAK,Eun,ASONA,Pinku
synopsis: I will marry you, but I have no intention to share a bed with you.The charismatic princess of Bashar meets the sharpest sword of the empire!The life of the two newlyweds united for alliance is a battle in itself.The tingling thriller of a romance between two brave and beautiful individuals who have never loved unfolds!

title: Adopted by a Murderous Duke Family
author: Rogang,URang,DaWoo
synopsis: After ten years of being exploited by Duke Gerwehr for her healing powers, Agnes meets her death in a dungeon. When she wakes up, she finds herself in her uncle house before she was sold to Duke Gerwehr in the slave market. Desperate for her past life not to repeat itself, she lets Duke Rodwick adopt her and starts her new life with a new name, Tuariche Rodwick. Will she be able to keep her healing powers secret in this notorious family of assassins and find true happiness and love in her new life?

title: Back From Black
author: M3,NADNF
synopsis: Zak, the greatest assassin to ever live, gets betrayed and killed, only to wake up two centuries later in a bioengineered body. Having been unable to save his wife and keep his promise to her, Zak uses his new body, and the Nanotechnology hidden within, to navigate through a new futuristic age of assassins and seek out the ones responsible for his tragedy.

title: Taming the Corrupted
author: LICO,Purple village
synopsis: Arlenne Serkia is granted the chance to go back in time and devises a plan to ruin the man who stabbed her heart. The key to her scheme is the Kasadin, renowned for his unmatched swordsmanship and stunning beauty. As the only child, Arlene realizes her family and position is at a disadvantage and she convinces her father to take Kasadin in to act as her sword and shield. But Kasadin has a past much deeper and more dangerous than she realizes and this drives his own motives for staying close to her, both personal and political. If Arlenne isn careful, the user might end up being used!

title: Memorial
author: sangC
synopsis: In a future where the world has been devastated by a deadly gas called Izpo, Minhui and his friends find themselves embroiled in a thick conspiracy where the stakes are high, and bets are made with one life. Only the Memorial Chips guard humanity against the lethal gas that permeates the atmosphere. But are these electronic securities truly built to guard us or watch us?Follow Minhui as he examines what reality is, and comes facetoface with the truth that will change him forever.

title: The Killer Shopping List
author: Kang Jiyoung,Jung Seokhyun
synopsis: Eunji Cha suffers from an undiagnosed medical disorder and frequently experiences violent seizures. After enduring years of abuse by her parents she wakes up from one particular episode and discovers the horrible truth behind the peculiarities of her family. The scars left on her mind after that day forever shape her character as she battles her inner demons and tries to keep her fiendish desire to murder at bay. Years down the road, her fate becomes intertwined with a man whose very nature is a stark reflection of her own. Will Eunji be able to contain the darkness within her? And will she come out on top in this perilous game of catandmouse?

title: The Last Adventurer
author: Blue Lobster,Dedart,Salty Dog
synopsis: In the Era of Adventure kickstarted by the spawning of Gates, marked by absolute hopelessness, destitute, desperation, and despair, everyone had given up their hope and lost their courage to continue fighting except one adventurer that refused to go down until his last breath."You are the only one left, Last Adventurer Elpam."As the history of adventurers was forced to come to an end, the Last Adventurer returned to where this story all began.

title: Roots of the Heart
author: Mewmimiu
synopsis: William is a city boy who has just turned 18. He finally old enough to do everything he wants, right? But his life is turned upside down when his family moves to the country, putting the brakes on all his big plans. Will he resist his new life, or will he let new relationships in?

title: Boy-Friend's Rule
author: Do yoon
synopsis: Jiun's first romance ends when her crush, Jaei, confesses that he likes someone else. To make matters worse, Jaei mistakenly believes that Jiun's crush is his scarylooking best friend, Seohyeon, and tries to help her win him over. Now, Jiun must deal with a bigger problem than her unrequited crush, the boyfriend she had never imagined getting close to.

title: Return of the Gods
author: HONGMUJE
synopsis: Uju Hyeon dreams of living the ordinary life of a high school student, but his dream will never come true as he possesses special powers that others don have. One day, after being chased by an evil spirit, he is taken to the School of the Tiger and learns that he has a dragon orb in his body. Will Uju be able to protect himself and the dragon orb from evil spirits?

title: My Exes Fell for Me
author: hee_ddok,HADA
synopsis: How awkward would it be to reunite with not one but two of your exboyfriends, and at the workplace nonetheless? When Nabom Han comes facetoface with her unforgettable first love, Chajun, and her exboyfriend she hoped shed never see again, Taeo, she must learn to navigate the relationships from her past while ensuring the success of her father struggling manufacturing business. They say you should never mix business with pleasure, but will Nabom be able to resist the temptation?

title: Onsaemiro: Never Changing
author: YeoWoo,SaMoon
synopsis: Haeri Jin is an aspiring actress who hasn't had the best of luck. But this time, she has a good feeling about the show she's about to audition for. Since it's a period piece, she decides to stop by a historical museum and comes across a beautiful incense burner from the Baekje era. Mesmerized, she prays for good luck, but little does she know that she has awoken a god named Onsaemiro who was trapped in the incense burner. How was she able to free him? Because she is the reincarnation of a princess of Baekje who was once Onsaemiro's lover!

title: Insector
author: MarkerBeam
synopsis: Humans are no longer at the top of the food chain. The creatures known as Insectors hide amongst us, using their supernatural insectile powers to prey upon humans. Miseong, a seemingly ordinary high school student, is also secretly an Insector. But unlike others of his kin, he directs his powers not at humans, but at Insectors instead. Will he maintain control over his abilities and use them for the good of mankind, or will he succumb to the monster within him?

title: Persona 3 Reload: Beginnings
author: Merryweather Media
synopsis: Hidden between one day and the next is a mysterious phenomenon called the Dark Hour: a time period where otherworldly creatures prey on human psyches, leaving behind victims with the debilitating Apathy Syndrome. In the midst of this darkness, the unknowing secondyear transfer student Makoto Yuki arrives at Gekkoukan High School and through a chance encounter, or perhaps fate itself, awakens a new power within

title: The Reborn Young Lord is an Assassin
author: swingbat,CoffeeLime
synopsis: Cyan Vert, illegitimate son of the Duke and the empire's greatest assassin, is betrayed by the righteous brother whose shadow he's always lived in. But just before the fatal blow strikes his throat, Cyan awakes to find he's just a boy again. The young lord has been reborn, and this time, he's not going to live in anyone's shadow!

title: Stalker x Stalker
author: Merryweather
synopsis: What happens when two yandere stalkers fall in love with each other?

title: Paranoid Mage
author: InadvisablyCompelled,Kisai Entertainment,WmW
synopsis: Callum has seen strange things all his life monsters, beasts, and mages secretly living among people. But even after awakening his portal magic, Callum has no desire to be any part of it.The Guild of Arcane Regulation demands fealty, education, and service of every new mage. To hell with that. If they want Callum, they'll have to catch him first.

title: A Spell for a Smith
author: ArtSasquatch
synopsis: A shy witch in her quiet forest cottage. A surly dwarf in his blacksmith's forge. Both seeking solace in their respective refuge, but both aching for more. Though drawn to each other's kindness, they can't deny the gentle chemistry simmering beneath their every interaction just as their secrets do.This series contains themes regarding anxiety, mental health, and selfharm that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: My Super Eldritch High School Melee Festival
author: HannesRadke
synopsis: In just a few days, the Eldritch Melee Festival at Cambia High School will begin. Fighters of the Four Houses will test their skill in the martial and metaphysical arts. Leyla and her BFF Tama want to spend the day like normal school girls for a change, but Leyla finds two suspicious love letters in her locker

title: Zombie Revelation: 82-08
author: Dal ah,Kyung woo,Park's Office
synopsis: A mysterious virus breaks out on board the Boat 8208 out at sea. The people who find out about it first only want to use it as a weapon but quickly lose control over the virus. Will the Trio survive long enough to rejoin their friend Jinu? Or will it be Jinu who doesn make it out to meet his friends?

title: One Step Closer to the Demon King
author: UNONG
synopsis: When the infamy of the Demon King echoes to the ocean's depths, Yuria, the king of the sea, decides to venture onto land and challenge them. However, the very act of gaining two legs robs her of all her power, transforming her into a helpless child. Now faced with this unexpected twist of fate, can Yuria rise above this setback and defeat the Demon King to claim her place as the most powerful being in the world?

title: The Price Is Your Everything
author: Gones,Haco,stu.neulbom
synopsis: Transported back to her first academy days, Nerys Truydd revisits a life marred by betrayal and torment. Exploited and poisoned by her own family and husband, her demise was met with a vow to curse those who wronged her. Now granted a second chance, Nerys vows to rewrite her fate. As she navigates her past, memories of those who hurt her flood back. Determined and fueled by retribution, she seeks to reclaim all she lost. Can she overturn her tragic past and emerge victorious from the shadows of her betrayal?

title: God's Gambit
author: 2HD,Bsamong,SECAN STUDIO
synopsis: Do gods play dice with the fate of entire cities?Yul Choi city is suddenly transported to become a piece in a board game of the gods. Just when Yul thinks he can work together with people to overcome the monsters and challenges, he realizes he must become the city greatest villain to save the city. Can Yul rise to the demanding task of becoming the greatest and most villainous hero his city has ever seen?

title: The Silent Warrior
author: Team Maetgamari,ANomad,Kim hakyoung,ROAD WARRIOR
synopsis: "Face your destiny." In the alternate realm of the Otherworld filled with creatures and Earth's catastrophes an ancient warrior, a human summoned long ago into the realm, is determined to bring it all to an end. Fueled by the resentment of an unknown past, this journey unravels hidden identities, embarks on undercover missions, faces death trials, navigates through betrayals, and wades through bloodbaths. What do the shadows conceal, and what destiny awaits in the heart of the unknown?This series contains graphic depictions of extreme violence, body horror, and disturbing imagery. Viewer discretion is advised.

title: Surviving a Harem
author: Jeonboon
synopsis: Jun Yu, a WBA lightweight champion, gets dumped by his girlfriend, then gets hit by a car and wakes up in a dating simulation game as Yujun Russell, the adopted DAUGHTER of a noble family! The game tells Jun that he can be reincarnated, but only after playing to win over the love of his target characters. Determined to see his exgirlfriend again, he eagerly accepts the challenge. Will Jun be successful in winning the hearts of his suitors, and manage to return to the world he came from?

title: Chocolate Snow
author: kandyxxx_
synopsis: Daejoon, while drunk, mistakes Aoi for the person he likes. Aoi plays along initially, letting Daejoon believe he is the one he desires. However, after hearing Daejoon's story and understanding his feelings, Aoi decides to change his approach. He starts to develop genuine feelings for Daejoon and wants to become his lover, setting the stage for a potential change in their relationship dynamic.

title: City Vamps
author: seashell_arts
synopsis: Adam, a halfvampire living with his father in the city, eagerly anticipates gaining full vampire powers at a certain age. However, upon turning 17, he grapples with the challenges of controlling his abilities and navigating complex emotions, such as love

title: So Not My Type
author: prollycarmen
synopsis: What's your type? Sixteen university students with wildly different personalities come together to experience all that college has to offer: stressinducing deadlines, exhilarating parties, odd roommates and of course, love.

title: Mono and Mochi
author: omumoo
synopsis: Having a cat is a huge responsibility, especially if that cat is Mochi! Mochi is chaotic, unpredictable, and hard to controlbut at the end of the day, Mono wouldn't trade him for the world.

title: Don't Read This
author: I Drink Mercury
synopsis: There is no story to read here. (Interactive)This series contains themes regarding mental health and anxiety that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Bunny Girl and the Cult
author: Merryweather
synopsis: Strange bunny girls have been appearing all over the city, attempting to recruit people into a mysterious cult known as "The Warren Divine".

title: The Stellar Swordmaster
author: Hong Dae Ui,juno,Q10
synopsis: The socalled Lighthouse of the North,the prosperous trading town of Schoarra, hides a dark underbelly: seedy slums ruled by five ruthless crime bosses. When streetwise orphan Vlad finds the brothel he works for decimated by a disgraced knight, he turns to the path of the blade, pledging himself to the pursuit of power by sword. Blessed with the ability to seek wisdom from his sentient sword, Vlad embarks upon a journey of growth and peril as swordsman in service to the powerful House Vayezid.

title: The Seductive Wife
author: Yoon Soda,RedpeachStudio
synopsis: This series contains themes regarding domestic abuse, sexual content and themes that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised.Some marry for love, and some marry for convenience. In Ijae case, she marries Yuheon, the son of a business tycoon, to save her family after her father ends up in deep debt. Even though their marriage is contractual, Ijae feels an intense attraction for the cold and calculating Yuheon. Every night in her dreams, she imagines what it would be like to make love with him until one day, the two end up actually sharing a passionate night together. But will their physical chemistry be enough to build a genuine connection? Or will Ijae remain a pawn in Yuheon game?

title: Night of the Goblin
author: munsik,dool
synopsis: Until just a few days ago, Siu Choi was your typical high school student. But suddenly he finds out he a descendant of the goblin clan, and thus a halfdemon.In a dark realm of another world there lives the Demon King, the demon who rules over the night and reigns over all demons of the world.Now, the fight for the throne begins.

title: This is a Campus Romance Series
author: Kite
synopsis: My name is Hayun Lee, and I'm an ordinary college student. I decided to go on a spontaneous trip before school resumed and met this guy named Kangon. He asked me out on the first day we met, but of course, I rejected him. I thought I'd never see him again, but guess what? I ran into him during the school club recruitment event! And wait What? Even Jiil, the president of the student club "You," also has a crush on me?! I swear I'm not delulu. I swear!

title: Hardcore Leveling Warrior: Earth Game
author: Sehoon Kim
synopsis: Im back! After a comet collides on Earth, a gaming world filled with monsters and dungeons becomes a reality. Amidst the chaos, Ethan wakes up as Hardcore Leveling Warrior, an almighty game character with exceptional luck and power. Once again, he will embark on a journey to become the strongest but this time, on Earth!

title: Mage and Mimic
author: Feathermage
synopsis: Muir the Mimic is tired of living her life in a dungeon. She wants to see the world and explore, and Rowan the Mage might just be her ticket out. But things are rarely that simple. When her goal is in reach a wicked curse tosses a wrench in things. But together maybe the Mage and the Mimic can find a way to have it all!

title: Zombie Wife
author: JD Lareva
synopsis: In a remote cabin in the woods, a man named Milton lives a quiet life with his wife, Shauna. Everything is what he could have dreamed for! except for the zombification of his better half. But despite this, Milton does not give up the future he dreamed of. Is he the most devoted husband ever or is he just plain crazy?

title: Lemon Soda & Coffee
author: made_by_cecilia
synopsis: When you notice a pretty stranger on the streets, chances are youll never meet them again. Youll just walk by and continue your normal flow of life Axel pipe dream of seeing his pretty stranger again is, for better or worse, met with an extra package.

title: The Primal Hunter
author: MAGNOZZ,Zogarth,AETHON,WmW
synopsis: Jake, a seemingly average office worker, unexpectedly finds himself thrust into a fantasy world teeming with dangers and opportunities. Rather than succumbing to fear, Jake thrives in this unfamiliar realm. As he navigates the expansive multiverse, his power grows and he transforms evolving from a mundane office worker into a true apex hunter.

title: Paperteeth!
author: Wulvert
synopsis: Avery is a vampire hunter! Who unfortunately gets bitten by and subsequently turned into, a vampire.

author: TerraTerrific
synopsis: As an angel of death, Eden is tasked with fetching human souls and leading them to judgement before they can transform into monstrous creatures known as Unresteds. He hopes his job will be easier when Celestino joins the crew, but the aspiring angel of music has other goals and refuses to cooperate. With the Unresteds growing stronger by the day, Celestino, Eden, and the other death angels must work together or face the same fate as their predecessors.

title: Snowbound
author: Kisai Entertainment,WmW
synopsis: A WEBTOON ADVENT CALENDAR! Two college enemies become trapped inside their university when an avalanche hits. Sage, a studious good girl, wants to escape before Christmas Day but, along the way, forges an unlikely companionship with Jackson, the slacker who always gets on her nerves. As their situation becomes ever more dire, they uncover each other's unexpected secrets while racing the clock.

title: Steel-Eating Player
author: Director9,JJJ
synopsis: Steel Emperor Hyeonuk Lee, the last savior of humanity, has died.The place he returned to in order to change the future is the military?!!Why here of all places?!Corporal Hyeonuk Lee's steel eating show begins as he rapidly grows to get revenge!

title: Love or Attraction
author: Yuu,Myeong
synopsis: Is it truly love without physical attraction? Byeol dumped her boyfriend after a disappointing night in the bedroom, whereas Gyeol got dumped for being "too much." These two, with clashing ideas about love, are set together to work on the student council. Will their misunderstandings only deepen the rift between them, or will they come to learn from each other?

title: I Give You My All
author: seokyeong,mangnanyong,jaeheemon
synopsis: Sehui Yun, a promising designer, lives as nothing more than a puppet for her family and is under the constant watch of her abusive stepmother. One day, she meets a seemingly perfect man, Taehyeong Han, who offers her an amazing job to free her from her shackles. However, it seems he may want more than just a standard work relationship.

title: Weapon Creator
author: Cookie poet,Borem
synopsis: Here, try this sword. Junseo Shin is a master weapon creator doing menial jobs to keep a low profile in a world teeming with monster dungeons. But his habit of lending weapons to those in need exposes him to mega guilds and covert figures out to kill budding heroes from his past life. Can Junseo craft his way out of trouble and uncover the conspiracy that followed him to this life?

title: Bad Ending Maker
author: SHIM JAE YEONG,519,RyuMo
synopsis: Mincheol game Wings Online is going to be ruined for the sake of profit! But the new General Director has forgotten one thing: Mincheol knows every nook and cranny of his virtual world. Together with his trusty AI sidekick Oasis, will Mincheol be able to enact his revenge and create a Bad Ending for Wings Online season 6 update?

title: I Will Live the Life of a Villainess
author: massi,TARU,mintberry
synopsis: After a fatal car crash, Yuna Jeong awakens in the body of Elena Rosaria, a character in the novel she read in her previous life. But there's a twist Elena is no ordinary character. She a notorious villainess who meets a grim end. Now, Yuna must alter her destiny in a chaotic world and find her way in this new life. Can she rewrite her destiny amidst the surrounding chaos?

title: Cinderella Boy
author: Punko
synopsis: [Comedy / Romance] When a fameobsessed boy named Chase finds a key that allows him to walk into any storybook and take the place of a character in it, he offered a chance to earn a wish for anything he wants. The only catch? He's always the heroine! Meanwhile, other forces are searching for his keyespecially Chase rival, a handsome but malicious young man in possession of another key, who is determined to kick Chase out of the storybook biz for good.

title: Following Eunju
author: Cherry Lee
synopsis: "This series contains themes regarding mental health, sexual violence and child abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/)." Minjun sets up a fake profile to get Eunju, his crush, to accept his follow request on social media. Now, with her daily activities and whereabouts available at his fingertips, he uses this information to move in as her nextdoor neighbor. But little did Minjun know, that Eunju life isn anything like what she posts onlinethis sends him down an unexpected path, where he learns that following Eunju turns out to have its consequences.

title: Obsidian Bride
author: V0RA,Chung purm,Team Quartz
synopsis: For all her life, poor Lueri has been hanging by a thread, and the situation doesn't get any better when she is forced into an unwelcome marriage. But by miracle or design, a magical invitation presents her with a way of escaping her loveless life by joining the empire Jewel Box. There, among the brilliant gemstones, she finds help in the unlikeliest of places, friends from the unlikeliest of crowds, and perhaps, something she been desperately yearning for until now true love.

title: Spore
author: Lee kang
synopsis: One day, an unidentified flying object appears in the sky along with unknown insectlike monsters. A normal high school student, Seungho Yun, is trying to survive as well as find his family. Along the way, he is aided by a message that tells him the future that only appears in his head. As he moves on with that slight advantage, he finds out that there are others who are getting the same message as him. Will he be able to find his family? And where are the messages in his head coming from?

title: The World of Dating
author: Yullo
synopsis: The series contains themes regarding excessive alcohol consumption that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. The day Seul declares that she will stay single, three attractive men suddenly decide to pop into her life all at once. A man who matches her ideal type, a childhood friend she known for twenty years, and a man who checks off all the right boxes. Will Seul be able to hold firm to her declaration of staying single?

title: The Outcast is a Fighter
author: kim ggulbal,Almond bread
synopsis: Mugyeol Cha, a highschool student, is consistently bullied by a group of delinquents at school. Elsewhere, Mugyeol, a mixed martial artist, has been set up to be left paralyzed and meets his demise. Two different lives are at their ends, but somehow, they both end up living on in the same body. Will they succeed in finding justice, and climb their way back up to achieve their dreams?

title: Wedding Strategy
author: YOOLMOO
synopsis: Haru has a secret. She has the ability to go back to a fixed point in time every time she gets married. One moment, Haru is standing at the altar. But suddenly, she back on the subway on her way to work. But this secret of hers turns out to be not so secret after all. Oneul, who has the same ability, meets her and tells her that she and Oneul are both players in a dating simulation game. Will they be able to see the game to its end by getting married to their main storyline characters and escape from the time loop?

title: Skylie
author: Sevmikyu
synopsis: On the last day of school, two girls decide to ask each other out. Katie, who is still unsure of herself and Skylar, who is very sure of herself. Can they make their newly formed relationship work? Read and find out!

title: Flower Pot Crew
author: Cute Prawn Studios
synopsis: Casper's father was a father only in name the man never showed him love, and his mother had mysteriously disappeared. Knowing how to care was never a priority, so being part of a gang was perfect for Casper until they decided to sabotage him. With no money, friends, or family, a cheery Ben suddenly shows up in his life. As their story begins in sunny Singapore, will the coldhearted Casper escape his tortured past and finally learn how to love?

title: The Mafia Nanny
author: sh00,Violet Matter,roousuu,Drawniels,WmW
synopsis: Being an Elite Nanny is simple: protect the charge, obey the principle, and don get emotionally attached. Easier said than done when Davina first client is a dangerously compelling Venetian underboss who determined to get under her skin. What he wants from her, she can imagine, but Gabriel Angelini drags her back into the glittering world of organized crime she thought shed left behind forever. She might get answers about her past if she digs deep enough, but can she protect Mikey from his father ambitions and keep her heart from getting tangled up in their treacherous web?

title: Bailin and Li Yun
author: Jayessart
synopsis: Dr. Li Yun is doing research in the arctic when he meets a strange, injured creature named Bailin. Discovering a mythical species might be the dream of every scientist, but will Bailin be a bit too much to handle? The arctic has never felt so warm.

title: I'm Dating a Psychopath
author: NoSleepAreWe
synopsis: When a new serial killer arises in her city, Finn suspects that he may be related to her past. Against her better judgement, she decides to pursue him in hopes of finding answers. Shortly after, Finn meets Isaac, who reminds her too much of the mysterious boy from her past

title: Secretly More Powerful than the Hero
author: HHAANN,LIMYE
synopsis: From a young age, I've always dreamed of being that unassuming hero,appearing ordinary but possessing unmatched strength. But one day, fate took a turn when I was hit by an eightton truck, and suddenly, reincarnation was on the table!What would you like to be in your next life? asked the goddess of reincarnation. Eagerly, I replied, I wish to become a wimp, but secretly OP!She granted my wish, but with an unexpected twist if anyone ever uncovers my true abilities, my heart will explode! This isn't quite the secretly OP wimplife I had in mind.

title: What the Evil Dragon Lives For
author: manubi,Honaran,Lemon Frog
synopsis: Unwanted from birth, illegitimate child Elaine Newt knows better than anyone that life not fair especially when she's chosen as a human sacrifice to appease the wrath of evil dragon Rabeth, who sworn vengeance on the empire for sealing him away for 500 years. But to her surprise, Rabeth grants her three wishes for waking him up from his slumber. When Elaine uses her first wish to stop Rabeth from destroying the empire, she finds herself transported back to the past with a chance to live her life all over again but this time, with a dragon by her side!

title: My Office Rebound Marriage
author: MIMIK,Lee Dalli
synopsis: Once the poster couple for office romance, Dawon and Taehyeon seemed unstoppable on their march to the altar. But when Taehyeon cheats on his fiancee with another coworker at K&C, Yujeong, their fairytale begins to unravel. Just when Dawon thinks all is lost, hope emerges from the most unexpected place, the office (again), and with the most unexpected personher boss, Junhu, known as K&C most eligible bachelor and the quintessential dreamboat! Could this twist of fate turn Dawon heartbreak into a fresh start?

title: Privacy Check
author: liggy,wachi
synopsis: Society is corrupt, but no society is as corrupt as Hanbit High School. Chaseong, a student at the bottom of the school social hierarchy, struggles to survive until he unexpectedly gains a mysterious ally who claims that together, they can uproot it all. But how? No one knows, but one thing is certain, Chaseong secret WeTube channel is about to go viral.

title: No Office Romance!
author: Dooboo,Namsoo
synopsis: Are first loves overrated, or can a reunion as adults bring back emotions of the past? Yunji and Saebom share a first love story left unfinished, abruptly interrupted by ten years of being apart. Now, as adults, both seem to have moved on from that unfinished chapter of their lives and agree to remain friends and coworkers. However, the surface is not everything there is to be seen, as an unspoken tension lingers between them. Will they merely stay friends, or does destiny have other plans for them?

title: Letters on the Wall
author: Jaelyngs,MissBlackClover
synopsis: After living 5 years in Spain, Tara returns to the hometown to obtain her bachelor's degree in the arts. Upon reuniting with her old friends and Emma, her best friend when they were kids, she will discover that everyone has moved on with their lives and that she seems to have been left behind. With a new romance hidden in the past between Emma and Tara, she will have to discover the real reason she returned to Manchester.

title: The Age of Arrogance
author: SOY MEDIA,Hansol,Lemon Frog
synopsis: After winning a long war, Asha Pervaz is expecting the emperor to compensate her with money. Unlike her expectations though, the emperor asks Asha to choose her own husband from a list of nobles. Asha chooses Duke Carlisle Haven, the emperor eldest son and former crown prince. Asha expects him to object and pay an alimony instead, but the duke actually agrees to marry her! He even promises to help Asha rebuild Pervaz. What does the duke really want? And will Asha get what she wants without getting embroiled in the growing royal conspiracy?

title: Elegant Desire
author: Kim Jong Geon
synopsis: What the chance of running into your first love again after twelve years? This is exactly what happens to Solhui after attending her frenemy bridal shower. What more? Her first love is having an affair with a married woman. But that not all. She meets him and the woman again when she starts a viola lesson with a new student.

title: Cross My Heart and Hope to Die
author: Baekhana,Yungeum,Yoo Yerang
synopsis: This series contains themes regarding suicide and mental health that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/). Silvia Florette wants nothing more than to die. In fact, most days, she can even be bothered to get out of bed. Sentenced to repeat life 99 times, she agrees to marry Duke Randall in an attempt to appease God and die at the earliest convenience. However, while Silvia is eager to consummate the marriage, her husband insists they must first fall in love before they can finally sleep together.

title: Here U Are
author: D JUN
synopsis: They say opposites attract, and that couldn be more true for Hyeonu and Jaehwan. Hyeonu is chatty and outgoing, while Jaehwan speaks in monosyllables and walks around with a perpetual scowl on his face. Although they get off to a rocky start, Hyeonu eventually learns that beneath Jaehwan reserved exterior lies a soft heart. Over time, the two slowly begin falling for each other but will their budding romance be strong enough to withstand all the obstacles thrown their way?

title: My Little Sister is the Demon Lord!
author: moodio
synopsis: After their parents' sudden passing, Gyeonwoo finds himself in the role of caregiver to his younger sister, who harbors a startling secret she's the Demon Lord with plans for world domination! Undeterred, Gyeonwoo is committed to nurturing his sister with love and guidance. Join them in this unique tale as they navigate everyday life amid their extraordinary circumstances.

title: Chronicles of the Demon Faction
author: FORCE STUDIO,codezero
synopsis: Tired of the yoke of the Divine Justice Alliance, master assassin Hajin Cheon attempts to flee, only to be confronted by martial artists of all allegiances, both orthodox and deviant. Succumbing to the wounds of his ferocious struggle for freedom, he awakens in the body of Ryang Seo, a prince of the notorious Heavenly Demon Cult who suffers from a disorder that prohibits him from the use of qi. In order to survive in his new life, Hajin must contend with the many dangers and enemies that lurk within the cult.

title: Hero the Maximum
author: JAEYI PARK
synopsis: Gangchi Han is a failed student who couldn excel in any field. His GPA hits the bottom, ranking last among his classmates. His skills, whether it is soccer or computer games, are scorned by his peers. Whatever he does, he doesn seem to do well. But he lately comes to a realization that his punching power is out of this world. With a little help from his father, the Handsome Bum, he enters the First Branch of Heroes. Now, the villains must shiver under his might, but will they?

title: Take My Money
author: AlohaDRY
synopsis: Prepare for some chaos as Miss Mina, a campus celebrity, stumbles upon her first love none other than the aloof senior who's as cold as an iceberg! She launches an extravagant mission, armed with both her heart and a bottomless wallet. Will her efforts and creative tactics crack his icy exterior?

title: Garden of the Dead Flowers
author: Sero,Corbenyx
synopsis: When she wakes up, Mila immediately notices that she has been inexplicably transported to the year 1940, during the time when the Dutch Colony was reigning supreme in Batavia. Confronted with this perplexing predicament, Mila is compelled to find a way to return to her own time. Yet, her efforts take an ominous turn as she stumbles upon a shocking scene a man, her very own grandfather, committing a heinous murder in his garden, where he proceeds to bury the unfortunate victim amongst his flowers.

title: Killer Peter
author: Kim Junghyun,Lim Lina
synopsis: After devoting his life to the crime organization, Glory Club, Peter retires his status as a legendary killer and spends his remaining days running a quiet used bookstore. But after being ambushed and nearly killed one day by the very organization he dedicated his life to, Peter finds his body magically reverted back to its teenage years. Now that Peter was back to his peak physique, he sets out to settle the score with Glory Club.

title: Cry, or Better Yet, Beg
author: VAN.J,Solche
synopsis: After losing her parents at the age of 12, Layla Llewellyn is passed from one uncaring relative to another until she sent away to another country altogether. Arriving in the Empire of Berg, she is placed in the care of Bill Remmer, a gruff distant relative who seems to care for little else other than his work as a groundskeeper for the renowned Herhardt family. After years of neglect, all Layla wants is a place to call home, but her encounters with the dashing Duke Matthias von Herhardt and the rest of high society pose trials and tribulations for the tenderhearted girl.This series contains themes regarding child abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Rental Hero
author: PORTO,KOBET
synopsis: Juwon Lee works as a doppelganger who poses as a hero alterego, and fills in for them in their social life while they perform their duties as heroes. One day, Justice, the strongest hero, approaches Juwon and requests his services with the promise of a hefty payment in return for his work. However, when Juwon arrives at their meeting spot, he is instead greeted by a completely unexpected sight

title: Cleric of Decay
author: bori,Senritz,YU,Sadadm
synopsis: Not all job classes are created equal! Marnac was pulled into a game while trying to play as one of its worst job classes, cleric of decay. Now he the only cleric of the Order of Decay, serving a goddess who been reduced to an animated hand that repeats the word MURDER!Will the Order last cleric become powerful enough before the prophecy of the end comes true?

title: Random Target
author: INE,Yuhan
synopsis: After the failure of her first love, Serin easily and quickly falls in love with any goodlooking guy. Two days before her birthday, she gets dumped by her hot boyfriend, and her search for a man like the legendary unicorn continues. Little did she know, she'd meet a real unicorn on the virtual reality blind dating app called Random Target. Is this app the golden ticket to finding her true love?

title: Ten Ways to Get Dumped by a Tyrant
author: danmyeong,mapzzil,Seo Gwijo
synopsis: Scarlett Arman is no ordinary lady, not just because she engaged to the emperor. Newly reincarnated as a character in a fantasy novel, Scarlett knows she is supposed to die a horrible death at the hands of her fiancee, Charleon Kalior. Determined to escape her fate, Scarlett decides to make Charleon break off the engagement But why does he keep wanting to spend time with her?!

title: I Hate That I Love You
author: Aericchi
synopsis: If he's a former gang leader, and she just wants revenge, then why is he living with her? And where are all these doki doki moments coming from??

title: Seagull
author: Tsubo
synopsis: Burnt out writer Kyle Anderson moves back to his home town after the death of his mother, only to find that the self proclaimed witch Mischa has taken an interest in him. With his life spiraling and his path unclear, Mischa helps him realize there's magic in the most unexpected places

title: The Devil Kiss
author: Kwak Dabin,Park Nahyeon,sparrowqueen
synopsis: On the brink of death, Eunji is approached by a handsome devil named Joshua, who promises her a second shot at life with a kiss to seal the deal. When Eunji wakes up to her secondlife, nothing seems different until Dojin, the human manifestation of Joshua, shows up at her school and starts following her everywhere she goes, turning heads and causing drama. Their honeymoon period is cut short when yet another devil, Sora, comes to ruin their fun. Can Joshua save his first love from the forces of Earth and hell?

title: Our Voice
author: Abyssal Team
synopsis: This series contains themes regarding anxiety, mental health and child abuse that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).Young Leopoldo Peralta was a child TV star who abruptly ended his career due to severe problems in his life. Leo lives with his friend Gaga, who supports and admires him. Despite his desire to live a life away from the cameras, both Leo parents and his friend will force him to continue his acting career, pushing him to confront prejudices, fears, and his traumatic past.

title: #muted
author: kandismon
synopsis: Jasper's heart lights up when he meets Kai, a boy who doesn't speak, and life becomes a little less lonely for them both. But when old wounds threaten to reopen, their evergrowing connection is put to the test. Will the silence stand in the way of their love, or will they find a way to communicate the feelings they both have?This series contains themes regarding mental health that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/).

title: Re:Trailer Trash
author: FortySixtyFour,Yishan Li,Alyssa Villaire,ManHe Studio,WmW
synopsis: Tabitha Moore has lived a miserable life of regret and being treated as "Trailer Trash Tabitha". But, after a mishap with an MRI, her mind is sent back to 1998 and into her 16 year old body. With her life now in front of her, maybe this is the chance to redo her life! But is it so easy to change what you already lived through?

title: Quantum Entanglement
author: Arts Angel
synopsis: An introverted physicist with anxiety and his extroverted friend end up with the ability to feel each other's emotions after a fourthdimensional experiment gets a little too handson. Sharing feelings has never been so complicated!

title: Cinder and Charm
author: Bryan Golden
synopsis: When you wish upon a pop star will dreams come true? 19yearold Cinder Glass dreams of a music career, but has had no luck in breaking out as a singer on social media, until one day his cover of pop sensation Charm's latest single goes viral. An opportunity arises, and Cinder's fairy tale ending might come true but only if he and Charm can stomach each other!Is his time up? Or are the idealistic Cinder and the jaded Charm actually a perfect fit?

title: WEBTOON at Midnight
author: WmW,RE ME,Kisai Entertainment,Arttricia00,Gabie Rivera,L.H.K Forney,Travis Brown
synopsis: A collection of original stories penned by r/NoSleep most twisted minds. Once you start, you may never sleep again. The series contains strong themes and graphic depictions of stalking, domestic abuse, and violence and may not be suitable for all readers. And if you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/ ).

title: Iseop Romance
author: 248,Anna Kim
synopsis: With her outstanding business acumen, Mingyeong Kang climbed the corporate ranks of TK Group, Korea top conglomerate, to become a senior manager in record time. But after 10 years at the company, she been assigned to be the secretary of Iseop Tae, the successor to TK Group. The two entered the company at the same time, but ever since he came second place to her at new employee training, Iseop never taken kindly to Mingyeong. She better than him in every way and trampled all over his ego so why can he stop thinking about her?

title: The Academy's Genius Swordsman
author: SeoGwando,C.H
synopsis: Following a momentous battle against giants for the fate of the world, Ronan emerges victorious as the last man standing of the imperial army. As he laments this hollow victory with his dying commander, Grand Marshal Adeshan, they quickly learn that the war is far from over and an overwhelming force of giants descends from the heavens. Fearing the worst, yet seeing hope in the courageous Ronan, Adeshan uses her last time slip to send him back to the past, so that he can enroll in the prestigious Phileon Academy and become the strongest swordsman the empire has ever seen!

title: Real World Mobile
author: KongE,Elko
synopsis: Gangu Choi is an ordinary high school student who likes video games. One day, he hears that his favorite game store is going out of business. When he visits the shop one last time, the store owner hands him a QR code for a mobile game. Gangu starts up the game out of curiosity, but something feels off. His mission is to drink 3 glasses of water?! When he decides to ignore the mission, he suddenly receives a penalty in real life!As the missions get more dangerous, will Gangu be able to protect his reality?

title: A Killer Paradox
author: kkomabi
synopsis: A man wakes up, tied to a crucifix. He a district attorney, held prisoner by a serial killer named Tang Lee. Why is he there? And who is this twitchy man staring him down?As the story unfolds, we follow Tang Lee descent from average nobody to murderer. The catch? All of his victims are revealed to be criminals, rapists, and killers who had escaped justice.Is Tang an angel of retribution? Or is it all in his mind? At every turn, a new dark corner of society decay comes to light in this twisted thriller.

title: Si Bel Homme List
author: LICO
synopsis: Ideum world turns upside down when her boyfriend of five years gets engaged to another woman, and even has the audacity to send her a wedding invitation! Shocked and humiliated, Ideum vows to get her revenge by showing up to the wedding with a hot new man on her arm. As a matchmaker at a marriage agency, she already knows many eligible bachelors, and can help but gush over her new client profile. Tall, handsome, and rich, Dr. Dohun Yang is just the man she looking for. But little does Ideum know that she in for a surprise in more ways than one.

title: This Wasn't My Plan
author: BOM SOHEE,SEI KIM
synopsis: In a twist of fate, Roa finds herself thrown back a decade in time. This isn't just a trip down memory lane. She's faced with a younger, naive Sihyeon, the future superstar who would brutally wrong her. Armed with knowledge of what's to come, Roa sees a golden opportunity: a chance to rewrite their history. Can she resist the allure of revenge and change Sihyeon's destiny before he becomes her nightmare?

title: Diving Into Love
author: ILGONG
synopsis: When her father tries to force her into financial independence and out of her bed, Taepyeong accidentally runs into a man who can turn into a fish?! To make matters more complicated, a cunning hotel president plots to take away her seafood restaurant. Now, Taepyeong has to find a way to save her restaurant and her love life all at the same time!

title: Rose and Sunflower
author: Paulina Majrquez
synopsis: All items keep memoriesand Luisa has the power to relive those precious memories, just by touching them. When Jaz and Dalia become her new neighbors, Luisa will try everything she can to get her hands on the valuable memories contained within their items. However, Luisa will find out these siblings hide more than memories[This series contains themes regarding depression, mental health and potentially disturbing imagery related to trypophobia that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. If you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/]

title: Like Mother, Like Daughter
author: YIDAHM
synopsis: Beautiful and intelligent, Somyung Gil has tirelessly strived to fulfill her mother's vision of the perfect daughter. However, when her lessthanperfect younger brother is tragically found drowned in a river, doubts plague Somyung's heart. She begins to suspect that their mother might be responsible for the unspeakable act. From then on, her paramount goal becomes escaping her mother's grasp, while all her mother wants is for Somyung to experience the perfect life she herself was denied. Will Somyung ever truly find her freedom? [This series contains themes regarding depression and mental health that may not be suitable for all readers. Viewer discretion is advised. And if you or someone you know is struggling or in crisis, please reach out for help at Crisis Text Line (http://crisistextline.org/]

title: My Sister Private Life
author: Jojuhee,Nureom
synopsis: A woman wakes up in a hospital with no memory of who she is. She doesn even recognize herself in the mirror.
